rticipant'),(2586,55,'_testimonials_0_testimonials_person','field_56d4618e4a309'),(2587,55,'testimonials_1_testimonials_quote','I’ve been on a gazillion diets over the years. This is the first program that provided a wonderful, healthy lifestyle approach — not just emphasizing weight loss. What a terrific experience this has been for me, as the quality of my life improved. '),(2588,55,'_testimonials_1_testimonials_quote','field_56d461824a308'),(2589,55,'testimonials_1_testimonials_person','“Mastering Weight Management” participant'),(2590,55,'_testimonials_1_testimonials_person','field_56d4618e4a309'),(2591,55,'testimonials_2_testimonials_quote','The hands-on stuff was great, particularly for dads.'),(2592,55,'_testimonials_2_testimonials_quote','field_56d461824a308'),(2593,55,'testimonials_2_testimonials_person','“Tool Kit for New Parents” participant'),(2594,55,'_testimonials_2_testimonials_person','field_56d4618e4a309'),(2595,55,'testimonials_3_testimonials_quote','I was able to start from where I was and make small changes. The coach had great suggestions, and it was very informative and helpful. I’ll be sure to share this with my husband.'),(2596,55,'_testimonials_3_testimonials_quote','field_56d461824a308'),(2597,55,'testimonials_3_testimonials_person','Health coaching participant'),(2598,55,'_testimonials_3_testimonials_person','field_56d4618e4a309'),(2599,55,'testimonials_4_testimonials_quote','I learned that I was doing many things that were undermining my own success! I now have a fresh start and clearer path to managing my diabetes.'),(2600,55,'_testimonials_4_testimonials_quote','field_56d461824a308'),(2601,55,'testimonials_4_testimonials_person','“Diabetes Basics” participant'),(2602,55,'_testimonials_4_testimonials_person','field_56d4618e4a309'),(2603,55,'testimonials_5_testimonials_quote','I have been able to modify much of my lifestyle. I lost weight and changed my eating habits. My health and quality of life has improved considerably. Thank you for 