festyle changes I wanted. It was so helpful to have someone holding my hand.'),(2624,55,'_testimonials_10_testimonials_quote','field_56d461824a308'),(2625,55,'testimonials_10_testimonials_person','Health coaching participant'),(2626,55,'_testimonials_10_testimonials_person','field_56d4618e4a309'),(2627,55,'testimonials_11_testimonials_quote','Changes were suggested in baby steps each week. Now I read labels; I eat vegetables and fruits, which I never did, and I’m not hungry (which was always an issue for me).'),(2628,55,'_testimonials_11_testimonials_quote','field_56d461824a308'),(2629,55,'testimonials_11_testimonials_person','“Mastering Weight Management” participant'),(2630,55,'_testimonials_11_testimonials_person','field_56d4618e4a309'),(2631,151,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(2632,51,'_genesis_noindex','1'),(2633,51,'_genesis_nofollow','1'),(2634,51,'_genesis_noarchive','1'),(2635,51,'exclude_local_search','1'),(2636,51,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(2637,73,'_edit_lock','1677822604:1'),(2642,382,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Anxiety'),(2643,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(2644,382,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Feelings of anxiety can interrupt your daily routine.\r\n\r\nTame your stress and take control.'),(2645,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(2647,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background_color','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(2648,382,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','145'),(2649,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(2650,382,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','Am I Experiencing Anxiety?'),(2651,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2652,382,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','Anxiety affects your thoughts, feelings, mood, and body.\r\n\r\nAnxiety can cause emotional and physical symptoms. These can include shortness of breath, irritability, panic, or dizziness, among others. When the anxiety passes, the symptoms stop.\r\n\r\nLearn more about the <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.anxiety.anxty#hw257184\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">physical and emotional symptoms</a> of anxiety.'),(2653,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2654,382,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(2655,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2656,382,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2657,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2658,382,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','Types Of Anxiety'),(2659,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2660,382,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=content:health-encyclopedia&amp;hwid=zd1045\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Generalized anxiety disorder</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=content:health-encyclopedia&amp;hwid=hw169097\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Obsessive-compulsive disorder</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=content:health-encyclopedia&amp;hwid=hw53796\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Panic attacks and panic disorder</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=content:health-encyclopedia&amp;hwid=zd1121\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Phobias</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=content:health-encyclopedia&amp;hwid=hw184188\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Post-traumatic stress disorder</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=content:health-encyclopedia&amp;hwid=hw177276\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Social anxiety disorder</a> (also called social phobia)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(2661,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2662,382,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(2663,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2664,382,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2665,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2667,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2668,382,'wellness_layout_topic','a:6:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";}'),(2669,381,'wellness_layout_topic','a:7:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";i:6;s:3:\"row\";}'),(2670,382,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2671,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2672,382,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2673,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2675,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2676,382,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','Should I Take Herbs Or Supplements To Help Reduce My Anxiety?'),(2677,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2678,382,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','The effectiveness of some herbs and other supplements is still unclear. They can also have serious side effects. Ask your doctor before using any to see if they are safe for you.\r\n\r\nVisit our <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://naturaldatabaseconsumer.therapeuticresearch.com/nd/search.aspx?referer=kaiserpermanenteconsumer&amp;lang=0&amp;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Natural Medicines Comprehensive Database </a>to find reliable information on herbs, vitamins, minerals, and other dietary supplements.'),(2679,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2680,382,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(2681,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2682,382,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','How Can I Help Myself'),(2683,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2684,382,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','There are many ways to alleviate the symptoms of anxiety.\r\n\r\nA few things to try include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.zq1031#zq1032\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Getting enough sleep</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.stress-management-breathing-exercises.ug1812?kpSearch=deep%20breathing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Deep breathing exercises</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://www.mayoclinic.com/health/meditation/MM00623\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Meditation</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.get-regular-exercise-for-mental-health.aa131383?kpSearch=exercise%20for%20mental%20health\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Exercising</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://thrive.kaiserpermanente.org/thrive-together/live-well/anxiety-stop-negative-thoughts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Change/choose your thoughts</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nView more tips about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.anxiety.anxty#hw257239\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">anxiety self-care</a>.\r\n\r\nKaiser Permanente members have access to digital mental health and wellness tools at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check out this page</a> for Calm, myStrength, or Ginger apps. You also can <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.'),(2685,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2686,382,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(2687,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2688,144,'_genesis_title','Manage Anxiety in a Healthful Way'),(2689,144,'_genesis_description','Anxiety can cause emotional and physical symptoms. There are many ways to alleviate symptoms. Learn more & take advantage of helpful resources.'),(2690,144,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(2691,382,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','144'),(2692,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(2693,382,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url',''),(2694,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','field_63ed55a382b95'),(2695,382,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(2696,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2697,382,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(2698,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2699,382,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','Sometimes, we all need a little help as we’re working towards a goal. As you work to alleviate anxiety, a health coach can help you work towards your goals, find new coping strategies, and keep on track.\r\n\r\nLearn more about Kaiser Permanente’s <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching</a> sessions.'),(2700,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2701,382,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(2702,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2703,382,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2704,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2706,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2707,382,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Is It More Than Anxiety?'),(2708,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2709,382,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','Anxiety disorders often occur with other problems, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mental health issues, such as <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-topics/emotional-health/depression/\">depression</a> or <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.substance-use-problems.center1035\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">substance misuse</a></li>\r\n 	<li>A physical illness, such as heart or lung disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Serious relationships problems, including <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.learning-about-domestic-abuse.abr9735?kpSearch=domestic%20abuse\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">domestic abuse</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(2710,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2711,382,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(2712,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2713,382,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2714,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2715,382,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','Meditation Can Help'),(2716,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2717,382,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','Interested in learning about additional therapies? <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/meditation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Meditation can help</a> alleviate symptoms associated with panic attacks and anxiety.'),(2718,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2719,382,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(2720,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2721,382,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2722,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2724,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2725,382,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','Your Total Health'),(2726,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2727,382,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','Remember, your well-being is affected by both your mind and your body. It’s important to take good care of each to have complete health.\r\n\r\nLearn how to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for the whole you</a>.'),(2728,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2729,382,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(2730,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2731,382,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2732,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2733,382,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','Looking For More?'),(2734,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2735,382,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','If you are a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member and want to discuss treatment needs or set up an appointment, please call the Mental Health Department, 1-855-632-8280.'),(2736,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2737,382,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(2738,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2739,382,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2740,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2742,382,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2743,384,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Depression'),(2744,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(2745,384,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Embrace the whole you.\r\n\r\nMental and physical well-being go hand-in-hand. Don’t let depression stop you from living life to its fullest.'),(2746,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(2748,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background_color','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(2749,384,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','160'),(2750,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(2751,384,'wellness_layout_topic','a:7:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";i:6;s:3:\"row\";}'),(2752,384,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','What Is Depression?'),(2753,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2754,384,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','Depression is an illness. It can cause intense emotional and physical symptoms. It affects your total health and well-being. If you’re struggling with depression, you may experience:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sadness or hopelessness that won’t go away</li>\r\n 	<li>Loss of interest in activities you’ve always enjoyed</li>\r\n 	<li>Physical signs like pain or feeling unusually tired</li>\r\n 	<li>Suicidal thoughts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDepression can be difficult to recognize–and hard to talk about. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://findyourwords.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Find help. Find hope. Find your words.</a>'),(2755,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2756,384,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(2757,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2758,384,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2759,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2760,384,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','Understanding Types Of Depression'),(2761,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2762,384,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.hw30709#hw30711\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Ongoing depression</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.bipolar-disorder.hw148751\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Bipolar disorder</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.seasonal-affective-disorder-sad.hw169553?kpSearch=seasonal%20affective%20disorder\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Seasonal affective disorder (SAD)</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=content:health-encyclopedia&amp;hwid=hw184188&amp;locale=en-us&amp;type=kb&amp;kpSearch=post-traumatic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Post-traumatic stress disorder</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGrief is not a type of depression, but its symptoms and treatment can be similar:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.grief-and-grieving.hw164282?kpSearch=grief\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">What is grief?</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.grief-coping-with-grief.aa122213?kpSearch=coping%20with%20grief\">Coping with grief</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/!ut/p/a0/LYtLDsIgFACvYg_w8lpNKbhDxAu4UNi9UKwvUtq0RK_vJy4nM4Mer-gzPXmgwlOm9GEXplxiLvuQaF2hj4U44QU9-sd8jrSEO7ph4Xjb_Iqv-C_co-t03YlWSThauYWmsQKUshZOptYHI8xOtgbncZQvXVVv20sucQ!!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Grief class and support groups</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(2763,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2764,384,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(2765,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2766,384,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2767,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2769,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2770,384,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','Is It More Than Depression?'),(2771,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2772,384,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','Depression can happen alongside other issues and conditions, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Illnesses like <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-topics/emotional-health/anxiety/\">anxiety</a> (an unusual level of worry or nervousness)</li>\r\n 	<li>A chronic condition, such as <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-topics/diabetes/\">diabetes</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.physical-abuse.viobh?kpSearch=physical%20abuse\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Physical</a>, <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.sexual-abuse-or-assault-rape.sabus?kpSearch=sexual%20abuse\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">sexual</a>, and/or <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.learning-about-domestic-abuse.abr9735?kpSearch=mental%20abuse\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">domestic</a> abuse</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://findyourwords.org/understanding-depression/related-conditions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Learn more about anxiety, chronic illness, and other factors that may contribute to depression.</a>'),(2773,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2774,384,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(2775,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2776,384,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2777,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2778,384,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','How Can I Find Out If I May Have Depression?'),(2779,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2780,384,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','If you’re 18 or older, you can <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/consumer/ancillary/!ut/p/a1/hY_BjoJAEES_xQNH071iCHIDE3VgVYxG2LmYEUec7DCQ2Y5Z_n4RYzy51q3S9VJdwCEHbsRVlYJUbYS-ee4dZvF2HUUfIa7HEx_ZcrqYslWCnSCDGHip62Mf_roQNYGDDha1IWnISnOSVloHgZMRlYT8R5E89OdfeocU1DYdosy5ttXzp_9r1AnyLE2DYJlFbB_P3NU7RNxrhCmU1sK23SreD0eXbfrh89RDZH6yS_aTxEUcPQIvFCI0ld-6-vops-H3JhwM_gDFfKKo/dl5/d5/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">take this self-assessment quiz</a>. You can also get more information on <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.hw30709#aa25747\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care and resources</a>. This is <strong>not</strong> a substitute for talking with your doctor, who can help you with treatment.'),(2781,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2782,384,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(2783,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2784,384,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2785,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2787,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2788,384,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GOK1tKFFIQI'),(2789,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','field_6402c9c746e19'),(2790,384,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-video\";}'),(2791,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2792,384,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','Is Depression Simply A “Chemical Imbalance” In The Brain?'),(2793,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2794,384,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','Depression is very complex. It involves brain chemicals like serotonin, brain cell connections, and much more. Understanding the science behind depression and its symptoms can often help those who suffer from it.\r\n\r\nWatch this video to learn more about what <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GOK1tKFFIQI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">happens in the brain during depression</a>.'),(2795,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2796,384,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(2797,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2798,384,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2799,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2801,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2802,384,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','How Can I Help Myself?'),(2803,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2804,384,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','Self-care can often make a big difference. If you’re struggling with depression:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.uf9919#uf9920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Use healthy thinking tools</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.get-regular-exercise-for-mental-health.aa131383\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Learn how exercise can help</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.meditation.aa141106spec?kpSearch=meditation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Empower yourself with meditation</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.stress-management-breathing-exercises-for-relaxation.uz2255?kpSearch=relaxation%20exercises\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Try some breathing relaxation exercises</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.hw30709#hw30709-HealthTools\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Use these health tools to help you make decisions or take action to improve your health</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.adaptive-health.com/intellicare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Try some apps developed by the Center for Behavioral Health Intervention Technologies, at Northwestern University’s Feinberg School of Medicine</a>. They are free from Google Play, and include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The Hub, to find apps based on your goals and to track your progress</li>\r\n 	<li>Thought Challenger, to reinforce positive thoughts</li>\r\n 	<li>My Mantra, for encouraging and reassuring messages you create</li>\r\n 	<li>Day to Day, for daily messages to help you apply new skills</li>\r\n 	<li>Worry Not, to learn to change negatives feelings that come from worrying</li>\r\n 	<li>Daily Feats, to help you add productive activities into your day and celebrate your accomplishments</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKaiser Permanente members have access to digital mental health and wellness tools at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check out this page</a> for Calm, myStrength, and Ginger apps. You also can <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.'),(2805,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2806,384,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(2807,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2808,384,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2809,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2810,159,'_genesis_description','Don\'t let depression stop you from enjoying life! Learn where to get help & how you can manage symptoms from Kaiser Permanente.'),(2811,159,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(2812,384,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_image','159'),(2813,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_image','field_63edb16465fe1'),(2814,384,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_url',''),(2815,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_url','field_63edb17765fe2'),(2816,384,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(2817,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2819,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2820,384,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','What If I Need Help Right Now?'),(2821,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2822,384,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','If you feel like you can’t cope, life is very difficult, or your life isn’t worth living, get help now.\r\n\r\nFor quick attention:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>If you’re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, call Kaiser Permanente Behavioral Health Crisis at <strong>503-331-6425 or 1-866-453-3932</strong>. It is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. Caring, experienced Kaiser Permanente team members will evaluate your situation and find the right care for you.</li>\r\n 	<li>Call the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline (available 24 hours a day). Local crisis workers will listen and help.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>1-800-273-8255</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>1-800-799-4889</strong> (TTY for hearing and speech impaired)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>'),(2823,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2824,384,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(2825,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2826,384,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2827,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2828,384,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','Depression And Abuse'),(2829,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2830,384,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','People who live with abuse often struggle with depression. If someone is hurting you, tell your doctor or call the National Domestic Violence Hotline at <strong>1-800-799-SAFE</strong> to get help.'),(2831,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2832,384,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(2833,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2834,384,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2835,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2837,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2838,384,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','Are There Any Other Ways I Can Get Help?'),(2839,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2840,384,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','As you deal with your depression, a health coach can offer support along with coping strategies.\r\n\r\nWe encourage you to learn more about <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">our health coaching sessions</a>.'),(2841,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2842,384,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background',''),(2843,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2844,384,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2845,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2846,384,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','Looking For More?'),(2847,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2848,384,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','If you’re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, you can discuss treatment needs or set up an appointment by calling the Kaiser Permanente Mental Health Department, 1-855-632-8280.'),(2849,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2850,384,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background',''),(2851,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2852,384,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2853,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2855,384,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2856,385,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Stress'),(2857,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(2858,385,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Tame your stress.\r\n\r\nStress affects the whole you – mind and body. Healthy thinking can help your relaxation response. Learn how to feel better by managing the stress in your life.'),(2859,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(2861,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background_color','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(2862,385,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','250'),(2863,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(2864,385,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','Why Am I So Stressed?'),(2865,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2866,385,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','Your body triggers an automatic response when you\'re afraid. The threat could be real or imagined. What can cause stress?\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chronic illnesses</li>\r\n 	<li>Emotional problems like grief or depression</li>\r\n 	<li>Relationship or work-related issues</li>\r\n 	<li>And much more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRepeated or uncontrolled stress can contribute to physical and mental disorders. These can include digestive problems, insomnia, cardiovascular disease, anxiety, reproductive disorders, headaches, chronic viral infections, depression, and diminished immunity.\r\n\r\nLearn more about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.stress-management.rlxsk?kpSearch=how%20stress%20affects%20the%20body#ta4209\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">stress and how it affects your body</a>.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-274\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/wlb09d041.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"360\" />'),(2867,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2868,385,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(2869,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2870,385,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2871,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2872,385,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','How Can I Help Myself?'),(2873,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2874,385,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','There are many ways to help alleviate stress:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.learning-about-mindfulness-for-stress.abs2092?kpSearch=stress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Practice mindfulness</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.learning-about-positive-thinking.abk7438?kpSearch=healthy%20thinking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Try positive thinking</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGet advice, encouragement, and tools with <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/healthylifestyles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">online wellness programs</a> that help you create positive changes in your life.\r\n\r\nOr try some apps developed by the Center for Behavioral Health Intervention Technologies, at Northwestern University\'s Feinberg School of Medicine. They are free from Google Play, and include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/thoughtchallenger\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Thought Challenger</a>, to reinforce positive thoughts</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/icope\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">iCope</a>, for encouraging and reassuring messages you create</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/relax\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Purple Chill</a>, for exercises on mindfulness, muscle relaxation, and visualization</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/slumber-time\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Slumber Time</a>, to get a better night\'s rest with a bedtime checklist, sleep diary, and an alarm you can customize alarm</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/dailyfeats\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Daily Feats</a>, to help you incorporate worthwhile and productive activities into your day</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKaiser Permanente members have access to digital mental health and wellness tools at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check out this page</a> for a 1-year subscription to Calm or myStrength. You also can <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for 6-month subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.'),(2875,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2876,385,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(2877,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2878,385,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2879,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2881,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2882,385,'wellness_layout_topic','a:5:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";}'),(2883,385,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(2884,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2885,385,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','Sometimes, we all need a little help as we’re working towards a goal. A health coach can be a valuable resource in your journey. A health coach can help you determine your patterns and behaviors, set goals, and find new coping strategies.\r\n\r\nLearn more about <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">Kaiser Permanente\'s health coaching sessions</a>.\r\n<h2>RELAXATION FOR LIVING AND SLEEPING WELL</h2>\r\nCultivating Health® <em>Relaxation for Living and Sleeping Well</em> guides you through several relaxation exercises.\r\n\r\nFind a quiet place where you will not be disturbed. Make yourself comfortable. Take slow, deep breaths. Listen and follow along:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/23QJaMrMPPT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Introduction/welcome</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-welcome-intro-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/HpGxGgKxt5N\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Daytime relaxation</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-daytime-relaxation-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/seOyacKRciQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Affirmations</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-affirmations-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/TTNUjo4JV2k\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Progressive muscle relaxation</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-progressive-muscle-relaxation-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/HKtLAI8YvRc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Relaxation for sound sleep</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-relaxation-for-sleep-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/hXxpUv1QqMz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Surf sounds</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRelaxation takes practice. The more you do it, the easier it will be to relax.'),(2886,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2887,385,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(2888,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2889,385,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2890,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2891,385,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','How Do I Manage Everyday Pressures?'),(2892,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2893,385,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Stress is often a result of our hectic lifestyles. Various responsibilities and rushing to do more with less sometimes means we sacrifice relaxation time with self and family.\r\n\r\nWant to learn how to cope better?\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.examining-your-beliefs-to-manage-stress.ta4960?kpSearch=live%20your%20values\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Live your beliefs and values</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Slow down and <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://thrive.kaiserpermanente.org/thrive-together/live-well/stress-management-managing-your-time\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">manage your time</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://tinybuddha.com/blog/feel-happy-and-stress-free-7-simple-tips-to-stay-in-the-now/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Enjoy each moment</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/relationships/how-to-learn-self-care?kpSearch=mental%20health%20and%20wellness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Practice self-care</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.work-life-balance-care-instructions.ut3350?kpSearch=work%20life%20balance\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Balance your work and life</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Please watch this fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_912319.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Tame Your Stress</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Por favor vea esta fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_912331.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Tome las riendas de su estres</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/finding-balance-stress-management-guide-spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Esta guía</a> describe cómo el estrés puede afectar su salud, y contiene recomendaciones que pueden ayudarle a sentirse menos estresado(a) en el trabajo</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/stress-management-workbook-spanish.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Use esta guía para el manejo del estrés</a>, la cual contiene encuestas, un diario, actividades semanales, y un plan de acción para el estrés</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I6402QJp52M\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Watch this video</a> to learn about the single most important thing you can do to manage your stress.</li>\r\n 	<li>Or, simply go for a walk to ease the tension.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(2894,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2895,385,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(2896,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2897,385,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2898,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2900,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2901,260,'_genesis_title','Stress & Emotional Wellness'),(2902,260,'_genesis_description','Feelings of stress can overwhelm your life & affect the whole you &#x2d; body & mind. Tame your stress by utilizing these tips & resources.'),(2903,260,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(2904,385,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','260'),(2905,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(2906,385,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:378:\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/consumer/ancillary/!ut/p/a1/hY9Lj4JAEIR_iweOplvxgdxQswr4wGgE52JmcdSJw0DGjpF_L2KMp13rVun6Ul3AIAGm-U2eOMlcc_X0rLf_CdbL4bDl4bIzcNCfj6YjfxFiJYghAHZS-W8d3p2JCtdCC9Nck9BkhD4II4yFwEjzTEBylST29flO35CUyqJCpD7mJvv89H-NPEASR5HrLvpeHAXdcfAN4a8arlOpFDdltYrVw9H2V_XwSdRD9J1wE24HoY3Yfgf-kIdQZE5pq9tMxM3Lyms0HuHnGUA!/dl5/d5/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/\";s:6:\"target\";s:6:\"_blank\";}'),(2907,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','field_63ed55a382b95'),(2908,385,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(2909,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2910,385,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','Breathing Exercises'),(2911,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2912,385,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','Did you know that breathing exercises can help manage intense emotions? Slowing down and focusing on your breathing instead of your worries can help you relax in minutes!\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/consumer/ancillary/!ut/p/a1/hY9Lj4JAEIR_iweOplvxgdxQswr4wGgE52JmcdSJw0DGjpF_L2KMp13rVun6Ul3AIAGm-U2eOMlcc_X0rLf_CdbL4bDl4bIzcNCfj6YjfxFiJYghAHZS-W8d3p2JCtdCC9Nck9BkhD4II4yFwEjzTEBylST29flO35CUyqJCpD7mJvv89H-NPEASR5HrLvpeHAXdcfAN4a8arlOpFDdltYrVw9H2V_XwSdRD9J1wE24HoY3Yfgf-kIdQZE5pq9tMxM3Lyms0HuHnGUA!/dl5/d5/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Watch the video now.</a>'),(2913,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2914,385,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(2915,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2916,385,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2917,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2919,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2920,251,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(2921,385,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Looking For More?'),(2922,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2923,385,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/insomnia?kpSearch=sleep\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Sleep well</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.ways-to-reduce-stress.av2185?kpSearch=ways%20to%20relieve%20stress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Simple ways to relieve stress</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.stress-management-breathing-exercises.ug1812?kpSearch=breathing%20exercises\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Breathing exercises</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.learning-about-guided-imagery-for-stress.abs1981?kpSearch=guided%20imagery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Imagine yourself well</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/reduce-stress/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/relax\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Create your own anti-stress plan</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RcGyVTAoXEU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Make stress your friend</a>, and use it to your advantage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf you\'re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, call 503-249-3434 or 1-855-632-8280 to discuss treatment needs or set up an appointment.'),(2924,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2925,385,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(2926,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2927,385,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2928,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2929,385,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','When Should I Seek Help?'),(2930,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2931,385,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','When stress begins to interfere with daily activities and overwhelms your life, try reaching out to others. Your family, friends, clergy, and health care team can all be of help.\r\n\r\nIf someone is threatening or hurting you, tell your doctor. Call the National Domestic Violence Hotline at <strong>1-800-799-SAFE </strong>if you need immediate help.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.interactive-tool-what-is-your-stress-level.zu1121?kpSearch=stress%20level\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Want to assess your stress level?</a>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-251\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/stress_topic2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"300\" />'),(2932,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2933,385,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(2934,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2935,385,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2936,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2938,385,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2939,380,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','How Does My Doctor Determine If My Child Has ADHD?'),(2940,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2941,380,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','ADHD can be misdiagnosed. A doctor should rule out other conditions by asking questions, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Is your child experiencing undetected seizures?</li>\r\n 	<li>Does your child have hearing problems, possibly an inner ear infection?</li>\r\n 	<li>And more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn more about ADHD and <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://www.nimh.nih.gov/health/topics/attention-deficit-hyperactivity-disorder-adhd/index.shtml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">symptoms, risk factors, and treatment</a>.'),(2942,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2943,380,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(2944,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2945,380,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2946,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2947,380,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','Are You An Adult With ADHD? Take The Self-Assessment.'),(2948,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2949,380,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Adults who believe they’re suffering from symptoms of ADHD can take a self-assessment to determine if they need to seek help from a medical professional.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://psychcentral.com/quizzes/addquiz.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Take the self-assessment now</a>.'),(2950,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2951,380,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(2952,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2953,380,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2954,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2956,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2961,380,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(2962,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2963,380,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','What Does Adult ADHD Look Like?'),(2964,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2965,380,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','ADHD in adults is slightly different from ADHD in children. See how ADHD often manifests in adults.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4VoZPxD22zM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Watch the video now</a>.'),(2966,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2967,380,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(2968,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2969,380,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2970,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2972,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2973,380,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','How Can I Empower My Child?'),(2974,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2975,380,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','Kaiser Permanente <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/static/health-encyclopedia/en-us/kb/supp/ort-/help/support-help.shtml#support-help-as\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Actionsets</a> are designed to help people take an active role in managing a health condition. Check out these Actionsets for ADHD:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.adhd-helping-your-child-get-the-most-from-school.tk1496?kpSearch=adhd%20helping%20your%20child%20get%20the%20most%20from%20school\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">ADHD: Helping Your Child Get the Most From School</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.adhd-helping-your-child-get-things-done.tk1723?kpSearch=ADHD%20helping%20your%20child%20get%20things%20done\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">ADHD: Helping Your Child Get Things Done</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.growth-and-development-helping-your-child-build-self-esteem.tk1326?kpSearch=helping%20your%20child%20build%20self-esteem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Growth and Development: Helping Your Child Build Self-Esteem</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(2976,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2977,380,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(2978,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2979,380,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2980,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2981,380,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','Is It More Than ADHD?'),(2982,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(2983,380,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','People with ADHD often have one or more other disorders. These include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.dyslexia.te7211\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Dyslexia</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.oppositional-defiant-disorder-odd-in-children-care-instructions.ut3161\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Oppositional Defiant Disorder</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-topics/emotional-health/anxiety/\" type=\"application/pdf\">Anxiety</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-topics/emotional-health/depression/\" type=\"application/pdf\">Depression</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(2984,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(2985,380,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(2986,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(2987,380,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2988,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(2990,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(2991,380,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','Are There Home Treatment Options?'),(2992,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(2993,380,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','There are many ways you can work on alleviating the symptoms of ADHD.\r\n\r\n<strong>A few things to try include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Taking care of yourself</li>\r\n 	<li>Staying organized</li>\r\n 	<li>Behavior management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGet insights and practical tips and tools on <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.nirandfar.com/best-articles/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">distraction, time management, and self-discipline</a>.\r\n\r\nView tips for <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.attention-deficit-hyperactivity-disorder-adhd-in-children-care-instructions.tw12189?kpSearch=ADHD%20home%20treatment\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">self-care at home to help your child</a> — and to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.adhd-taking-care-of-yourself-when-your-child-has-adhd.ue4903?kpSearch=ADHD%20take%20care%20of%20yourself\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">help yourself</a>.'),(2994,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(2995,380,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(2996,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(2997,380,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(2998,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(2999,380,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_image','139'),(3000,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_image','field_63edb16465fe1'),(3001,380,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_url',''),(3002,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_url','field_63edb17765fe2'),(3003,380,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(3004,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3006,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3007,380,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','Your Total Health'),(3008,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3009,380,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','Remember, your well-being is affected by both your mind and your body. It’s important to take good care of each to have complete health. Learn how to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/washington/health-wellness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for the whole you</a>.\r\n\r\nKaiser Permanente members have access to digital mental health and wellness tools at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\">Check out this page</a> for self-care apps Calm, myStrength, and Ginger. You also can <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.'),(3010,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3011,380,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background',''),(3012,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3013,380,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3014,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3015,380,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(3016,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3017,380,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','A health coach can help you work towards developing new behaviors, find new coping strategies, and keep you on track.\r\n\r\nWe encourage you to learn more about Kaiser Permanente’s <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching sessions</a>.'),(3018,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3019,380,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background',''),(3020,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3021,380,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3022,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3024,380,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3025,381,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Diabetes'),(3026,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(3027,381,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Get empowered.\r\n\r\nEven small lifestyle changes can help you manage your diabetes.'),(3028,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(3030,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background_color','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(3031,381,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','162'),(3032,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(3033,381,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3034,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3035,381,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3036,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3038,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_background_color_row','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3039,381,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(3040,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(3041,381,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background',''),(3042,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3043,381,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id',''),(3044,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3045,381,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class',''),(3046,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3047,379,'wellness_layout_listing_0_background','#00a19b'),(3048,379,'_wellness_layout_listing_0_background','field_63fbd5c26d0f8'),(3049,381,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','Could I Have Diabetes Without Knowing It?'),(3050,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3051,381,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','People often have diabetes long before any symptoms appear. If you have these symptoms, be sure to get checked for diabetes:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Frequent urination</li>\r\n 	<li>Excessive thirst</li>\r\n 	<li>Extreme hunger</li>\r\n 	<li>Weight fluctuations</li>\r\n 	<li>Fatigue</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn more about the steps our doctors take to<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.criteria-for-diagnosing-diabetes.tj4293?kpSearch=diagnose%20diabetes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\"> diagnose diabetes</a>.'),(3052,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'