 title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.hw135189#uq1459\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">help prevent diabetes</a>.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-244\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/sen05d001.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"360\" />'),(3092,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3093,381,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_background',''),(3094,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3095,381,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3096,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3097,381,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','How Can I Manage Diabetes?'),(3098,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3099,381,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','To keep your diabetes under control, it’s important to:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Eat healthy\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Check out this <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.learning-about-meal-planning-for-diabetes.abr8924?kpSearch=diabetes%20meal%20planning\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">meal-planning method</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://tracker.diabetes.org/my_mfa/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">Use Diabetes Food Hub</a> to set goals, analyze foods, save recipes and menus, and more</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://diabetes.org/healthy-living/recipes-nutrition\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">Try some recipes from Diabetes Forecast</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Please watch this fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_719691.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Eat Well with Diabetes</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Por favor vea esta fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_719697.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Coma bien con diabetes</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.interactive-tool-do-your-bmi-and-waist-size-increase-your-health-risks.tx4379\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Calculate your BMI (body mass index)</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:fitness&amp;article=9EE1CA8A-5E75-11E1-8875-FEE8063E94D5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Get regular exercise</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.tips-for-exercising-safely-when-you-have-diabetes.hw133134?kpSearch=exercise%20safely\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Exercise safely</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.home-blood-sugar-test.hw226531\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check your blood sugar</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Take care of <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">your body and your mind</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Please watch this fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_912244.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Help for Diabetes-related Depression</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Por favor vea esta fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_912249.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Hay ayuda si tiene diabetes y esta deprimido</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou can also talk with your doctor about whether medicine might help. Some people with diabetes use insulin:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Please watch this fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_719972.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Insulin Keeps You Healthy</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Por favor vea esta fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_715882.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">La insulina lo mantiene sano</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Watch this video on <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9uSSBu-5eSY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">how to prepare and inject a single dose of insulin</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Watch this video on <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cjMy-RLX3VE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">how to prepare and inject a mixed dose of insulin</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGet a <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.aace.com/disease-and-conditions/diabetes/are-you-prepared-manage-your-diabetes-emergency\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Diabetes Emergency Plan</a> to help you prepare for natural disasters or other emergency situations.\r\n\r\nCheck out this video about <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eN0maNygmd0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">“Three Things to Improve Your Diabetes.”</a>'),(3100,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3101,381,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(3102,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3103,381,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3104,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3105,381,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(3106,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3107,381,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','video'),(3108,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3109,381,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(3110,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3111,381,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_image','261'),(3112,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(3113,381,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_url','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:378:\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/consumer/ancillary/!ut/p/a1/hY9Bj4IwEIV_iweOZkYxBrghySp2V2s0C9uLqVi12VJId2Lk34uYjSf13V7mfXnzQEAOwsqzPkrSlZXm5sV4-zFfLyeTQYzLURhg-pXMknTBsBVkMAdxNNWuC_-ciOrIQw-LypKy5JTdK6echyDIylJB_qdJbbvzhd4hBTV1i2h7qFz5-Ol1jd5DnnEeRQtc80HI2TtC3lukLbQx0jXtKNHtRj9ddbunfIyYBmzDvkPmIw7_A08UI9Rl0Pjm_Kmy_u8q7vWuhPKhmg!!/dl5/d5/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/\";s:6:\"target\";s:6:\"_blank\";}'),(3114,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_url','field_63ed55a382b95'),(3115,381,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(3116,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3117,381,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','Create An Action Plan'),(3118,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3119,381,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0