text','It depends on the pregnancy. Some women can manage diabetes throughout their pregnancy with regular exercise and healthy food choices. Others may also need medication.\r\n\r\nIf you’re pregnant and managing diabetes, talk with your doctor to decide on the best treatment options for you.\r\n\r\nWatch this video about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/washington/health-wellness/videos/conditions-diseases/healthy-pregnancy-with-diabetes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">diabetes and pregnancy</a>.'),(3268,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3269,381,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(3270,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3271,381,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3272,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3273,381,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','How Can Kaiser Permanente Help Me?'),(3274,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3275,381,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','We offer <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/washington/health-wellness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">helpful information and resources</a> to help keep you healthy.\r\n\r\nKaiser Permanente members can get advice, encouragement, and tools at no charge with <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/healthylifestyles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">online wellness programs</a> that help you create positive changes in your life.\r\n\r\nFor digital mental health and wellness tools, <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">check out this page</a> for Calm, myStrength, and Ginger apps. You also can <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive. There is no charge.\r\n\r\nFor Northwest Region members, the <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/managing-diabetes.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Managing Diabetes and Insulin Information classes</a> are very helpful.'),(3276,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3277,381,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(3278,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3279,381,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3280,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3281,381,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background',''),(3282,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3283,381,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id',''),(3284,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3285,381,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class',''),(3286,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3287,381,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','Your Prevention Plan'),(3288,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3289,381,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','Staying well by preventing or delaying disease is possible with health screenings and immunizations. Prevention plans can be tailored to every member of your family.\r\n\r\nLearn more about preventive care.'),(3290,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3291,381,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background',''),(3292,381,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_c