rovide learning opportunities for a variety of health topics.\r\n\r\nWomen\'s health information:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.learning-about-menopause.abn1925\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Menopause</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.osteoporosis.hw131419\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Osteoporosis</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:senior-health&amp;article=49C2B586-6722-11E1-A0DD-EF0FC2D681D2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Bladder and urinary health</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWomen\'s health classes on bladder control and menopause are available. <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/classes/\">Check the class catalog.</a>\r\n\r\nAs you age, you can move forward positively by educating yourself!'),(3382,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3383,387,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(3384,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3385,387,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3386,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3387,387,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','What If I Want To Keep Living Independently As Long As Possible?'),(3388,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3389,387,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Even though your body changes as you age, those changes don\'t have to limit your independence. Take advantage of these services and resources.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:senior-health&amp;article=177972F2-6715-11E1-9B06-904DE8E6D7ED\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Staying independent at home</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:senior-health&amp;article=0B735AB8-6715-11E1-B482-80315CE603A9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Alternative living arrangements</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:senior-health&amp;article=9213C326-6712-11E1-B149-D2C363E92356\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Caregiving</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:senior-health&amp;article=29860E22-6A1E-11E1-BAEA-8885B8784F8C\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Planning ahead</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMaking informed choices and creating balance in your life can help you improve or maintain your health and independence.'),(3390,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3391,387,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(3392,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3393,387,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3394,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3395,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','#e6e6e6'),(3396,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3397,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id',''),(3398,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3399,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class',''),(3400,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3401,143,'_genesis_description','Maintain your health & and age gracefully by making informed choices. These resources offer tips about staying independent, fit & much more.'),(3402,143,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(3403,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','143'),(3404,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(3405,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url',''),(3406,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','field_63ed55a382b95'),(3407,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(3408,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3409,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','What Should I Do About Medical Care?'),(3410,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3411,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','Gather info and learn about your options to get the care you need so you can feel your best — in mind, body, and spirit — and maintain your vitality and independence.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.healthy-aging.tn9719#tn9727\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Getting the medical care you need</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/mental-health/how-to-get-care\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Mental health services</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.hearing-tests.tv8475?kpSearch=hearing%20evaluations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Hearing tests</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://nei.nih.gov/healthyeyes/eyehealthtips\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Eye health tips</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKaiser Permanente members can <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">log on</a> for a Personal Action Plan, community resources, health guides and more convenient online tools for members.'),(3412,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3413,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(3414,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3415,387,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3416,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3417,387,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(3418,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3419,387,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id',''),(3420,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3421,387,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(3422,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3423,387,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','I\'m A Caregiver, And Need Some Useful Resources'),(3424,387,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3425,387,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','There are many resources and classes available for caregivers. Both family members and professionals can take advantage of them!\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://oregoncarepartners.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Oregon Care Partners</a> offers free in-person and online classes. Topics include Alzheimer’s and related dementias, geriatric medication management, and challenging behaviors.\r\n\r\nYou can also get more tips and resources at:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.co.washington.or.us/HHS/DAVS/davs-calendar.cfm#/?i=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Washington County, OR, caregiver support group</a>s</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/he