ut_topic_5_col-left_0_text','Remember, your well-being is affected by both your mind and your body. Learn how to care for the whole you.\r\n\r\nKaiser Permanente members have access to digital mental health and wellness tools at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check out this page</a> for the Calm, Ginger, or myStrength apps. You also can <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for 6-month subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.'),(3586,388,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3587,388,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(3588,388,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3589,388,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3590,388,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3591,388,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','Looking For More?'),(3592,388,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3593,388,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','For information on area classes and other programs, <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://public.health.oregon.gov/PreventionWellness/SafeLiving/FallPrevention/Pages/index.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">check out the listings from Oregon Health Authority</a>.'),(3594,388,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3595,388,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(3596,388,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3597,388,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3598,388,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3599,391,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Exercise/Physical Activity'),(3600,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(3601,391,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Start with one step.\r\n\r\nExercise helps the whole you – body and mind. Learn how to set goals, stay motivated, and find activities you love.'),(3602,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(3603,391,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(3604,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(3605,391,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','168'),(3606,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(3607,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background',''),(3608,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3609,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id',''),(3610,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3611,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class',''),(3612,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3613,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','Should I Jump Right In To Exercising?'),(3614,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3615,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','When you start a new exercise program, it\'s tempting to jump right in. But if you push too hard, <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.fitness-getting-and-staying-active.ftpln#ug1852\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">you risk injuring yourself</a>.\r\n\r\nYou can also talk to your doctor before starting a fitness program.\r\n\r\nIt\'s OK to take small steps towards better health!\r\n\r\nGet advice, encouragement, and tools with <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/healthylifestyles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">online wellness programs</a> that help you create positive changes in your life'),(3616,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3617,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(3618,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3619,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3620,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3621,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','Find Your Motivation To Start Moving'),(3622,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3623,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/washington/health-wellness/videos/live-healthy/exercise\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Understand the benefits</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://shapescale.com/blog/fit-tech/the-future-of-fitness-how-technology-is-changing-your-workout-routine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Use technology to track progress</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.quick-tips-getting-active-as-a-family.zx3509?kpSearch=exercise%20with%20family\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Get active with family and friends</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.fitness-making-it-a-habit.zx3268?kpSearch=set%20fitness%20goals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Set fitness goals and build a habit</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/parenting/be-more-resilient\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Bounce back from a setback</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(3624,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3625,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(3626,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3627,391,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3628,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3629,391,'wellness_layout_topic','a:7:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";i:6;s:3:\"row\";}'),(3630,391,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background',''),(3631,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3632,391,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id',''),(3633,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3634,391,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class',''),(3635,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3636,391,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','How Can I Make Physical Activity A Part Of My Routine?'),(3637,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3638,391,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','Simple choices can add up to a more fit you. Park further from the grocery store for the extra steps. Take the stairs instead of the elevator. These choices then become part of your life.\r\n\r\nThen, start your journey with small steps, like <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.becoming-more-active-where-to-start.ack9342\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">creating a fitness routine.</a>\r\n\r\nLearn more about how to make exercise <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.fitness-getting-and-staying-active.ftpln#ta1572\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">part of your everyday life.</a>'),(36