Also check out:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.nia.nih.gov/health/publication/exercise-physical-activity/introduction\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">National Institute on Aging\'s Exercise &amp; Physical Activity Guide</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://exerciseismedicine.org/assets/page_documents/TEN%20FREQUENTLY%20ASKED%20QUESTIONS%20BY%20OLDER%20ADULTS%20ABOUT%20PHYSICAL%20ACTIVITY.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\" type=\"application/pdf\">Exercise in Older Adults—FAQ’s</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.physical-activity-as-you-get-older.abo3821?kpSearch=physical%20activity%20as%20you%20get%20older\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Physical Activity as You Get Older</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(3707,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3708,391,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(3709,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3710,391,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3711,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3712,391,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','Try A Video Or App'),(3713,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3714,391,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','Exercise videos and apps can help you learn about different activities, and teach you some new moves.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=808svcWW-Cs&amp;t=37s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Strengthening with a stretch band</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m7zCDiiTBTk&amp;t=155s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Seated exercise to boost cardio</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hIOHGrYCEJ4&amp;t=53s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Beginner\'s tai chi</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h6udf_EV3JU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Lower-body workout</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v7AYKMP6rOE&amp;t=40s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Beginner\'s yoga</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=irptqdkJ1lU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Zumba — basic steps</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://sworkit.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Sworkit</a> lets you customize a body weight workout from a database of videos</li>\r\n 	<li>Choose different poses and difficulty levels with <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://www.pocketyoga.com/Apps/PocketYoga\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Pocket Yoga</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Work all parts of your body in 12 movements with the <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://well.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/05/09/the-scientific-7-minute-workout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">7-Minute Workout</a> app</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3715,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3716,391,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(3717,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3718,391,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3719,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3720,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background',''),(3721,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3722,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id',''),(3723,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3724,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class',''),(3725,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3726,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(3727,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3728,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','Sometimes, we all need a little help. A health coach can help you set goals, find new activities to try, and keep you on track.\r\n\r\nWe encourage you to learn more about Kaiser Permanente’s <a href=\"https://healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching sessions</a>.'),(3729,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3730,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background',''),(3731,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3732,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3733,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3734,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','Do I Have To Watch My Diet Too?'),(3735,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3736,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','A healthy body is about exercise and physical activity, but it’s also about eating right. A good nutrition plan can keep your body fit and ready for anything.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-topics/healthy-weight/nutrition-healthy-eating/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Get more information</a>.'),(3737,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3738,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background',''),(3739,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3740,391,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3741,391,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3742,392,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Nutrition/Healthy Eating'),(3743,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(3744,392,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Nourish the whole you.\r\n\r\nNutrition and healthy eating are keys to your wellness journey. Every day, what you eat and the food choices you make directly impact your mind and body.'),(3745,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(3746,392,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(3747,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(3748,392,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','411'),(3749,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(3750,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background',''),(3751,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3752,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id',''),(3753,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3754,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class',''),(3755,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3756,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','What’S My First Step?'),(3757,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3758,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','The best step is to start by understanding where you are in your health and wellness journey. Knowing where you are starts with taking a total health assessment.\r\n\r\nThen, you can decide where to go next!\r\n\r\nIf you\'re a Kaiser Permanente member, <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-assessment\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">take the total health assessment now</a>.'),(3759,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3760,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(3761,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3762,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3763,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3764,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','Your Healthy Eating Toolbox'),(3765,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3766,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.webmd.com/diet/guide/the-truth-about-fad-diets#1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Do fad diets really work?</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.pennmedicine.org/updates/blogs/metabolic-and-bariatric-surgery-blog/2019/july/how-to-stop-food-cravings\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">How to curb cravings</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.nutri#zp3542\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Make change a habit</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe National Institutes of Health also has <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/educational/wecan/tools-resources/nutrition.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Nutrition Tools and Resources</a> for help with healthy eating.'),(3767,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3768,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(3769,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3770,392,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3771,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3772,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background',''),(3773,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3774,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id',''),(3775,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3776,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class',''),(3777,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3778,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','How Do I Get Started?'),(3779,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3780,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','You can eat healthier one small bite at a time.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.developing-a-plan-for-healthy-eating.ug2139\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Set healthy eating goals</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Track progress with a <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/daily_food_ex_diary.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">daily food diary</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/parenting/be-more-resilient\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Manage setbacks in a healthy, positive way</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Get advice, encouragement, and tools with <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/healthylifestyles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">online wellness programs</a> that help you create positive changes in your life</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3781,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3782,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(3783,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3784,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3785,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3786,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(3787,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3788,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Sometimes, we all need a little help as we’re working towards a goal. As you work to eat healthier, a health coach can help you work towards your goals and keep you on track.\r\n\r\nLearn more about Kaiser Permanente’s <a href=\"https://healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching sessions.</a>'),(3789,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3790,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(3791,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3792,392,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3793,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3794,392,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background',''),(3795,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3796,392,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','video'),(3797,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3798,392,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class',''),(3799,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3800,148,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(3801,392,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','148'),(3802,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(3803,392,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:378:\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/consumer/ancillary/!ut/p/a1/hY_BjoJAEES_xQNH061sELmBya44rmI0gnMxszjqxGEgsx0jfy9ijCe1bpWul-oCDhlwI87qIEiVRuib5972e7K