";}'),(3816,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(3817,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3818,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id',''),(3819,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3820,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(3821,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3822,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Are There Some General Good Eating Guidelines I Should Follow?'),(3823,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3824,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','<strong>Healthy eating can include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.webmd.com/diet/ss/slideshow-serving-sizes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Paying attention to portions</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.drinking-enough-water.abk5466\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Drinking more water</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.aa15626#aa15626-sec\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Choosing lean proteins</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.aa160619#aa160619-sec\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Knowing your fats</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health-topics/dash-eating-plan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">The DASH eating plan</a> is a flexible and balanced way of heart-healthy eating.\r\n\r\nThe <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://www.choosemyplate.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">USDA\'s My Plate</a> program provides recommendations for the right food and amounts for different audiences (children, students, adults, etc.).\r\n\r\n<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.eatgathergo.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/MeetingYourMyPlateGoalsOnABudget.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\" type=\"application/pdf\">This booklet </a>is full of tips, tricks, and recipes to meet your MyPlate goals on a budget.\r\n\r\nLearn more about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.weight-management.aa122915#aa126381\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">good eating guidelines</a>.'),(3825,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3826,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(3827,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3828,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3829,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3830,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','How Can I Cook Healthier?'),(3831,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3832,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','Eating healthier starts in the kitchen. A nourishing meal is easy to prepare when you have the right resources!\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.modify-recipes-for-a-heart-healthy-diet.ue4723abc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Update your recipes</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.healthy-eating-making-healthy-choices-when-you-shop.uz2171\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Shop smarter</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.quick-tips-making-healthy-snacks.ud3722?kpSearch=smart%20snacks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Prepare smart snacks</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.Quick-Tips-Making-Fast--Healthy-Meals.ud3717\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Make fast, healthy meals</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://cookingwithkids.org/recipes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Get the kids involved</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDid you know that half your dinner plate should be filled with fresh, delicious vegetables? Learn more about <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/kp-healthy-plate.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">how to set your plate</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Are there other online tools I can use?</strong>\r\n\r\nCheck out <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://about.kaiserpermanente.org/total-health/food-for-health\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Food for Health</a>. You\'ll find recipes and short essays about food and nutrition. There are also links to related sites, including these <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLXVDFpw1BnTyPMtzXc3y32R2-rZeXZkiJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">cooking videos</a>.'),(3833,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3834,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(3835,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3836,392,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block