joJAEISfxQNH041sFLmhyboj_mA0gnMxszjqxGEgY8fI24sY40mtW6XrS3UBhxS4ERd1EKQKI_Td8-72d7ycDwZuiPOfvo9sOvwbslmEtSCBMfCDLv6b8OZIVAYOOpgVhqQhK81OWmkdBE5G5BLSsyK5bc5X-oZkVJU1osy-sPnrp881agdpEsdBMMNl3Bu5zP2GiEeNMJnSWtiqXsWb4eixRTN8FHcRmR-tonU_8hA7z8AbhQhl7leevkxk0j4twlbrBqNXlZQ!/dl5/d5/L2dBISEvZ0FBIS9nQSEh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Watch the video now</a>.'),(3854,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3855,392,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(3856,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3857,392,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3858,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3859,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background',''),(3860,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3861,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id',''),(3862,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3863,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class',''),(3864,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3865,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','What\'s Plant-Based Eating About?'),(3866,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3867,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','Plant-based diets are based on minimally processed vegetables, tubers, whole grains, legumes, fruits, nuts, and seeds. Research has shown there are many health benefits to eating all or mostly plant foods.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/nf-103-plant-based-diets.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Types of plant-based diets</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/nf-104-plant.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Books and other resources</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/15116-plant-based-eating.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">“Plant-based Eating” booklet</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn more in “Plant-based Eating,” a 3-week series taught by a registered dietitian. Kaiser Permanente Northwest members can take this class online. <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/plant-based-eating-ppt-for-website.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Review the class presentation</a>. To register, call 503-286-6816 or 1-866-301-3866 and select option 2.'),(3868,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3869,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background',''),(3870,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3871,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3872,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3873,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','Can The Right Diet Really Improve Health Problems?'),(3874,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3875,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','Of course! Did you know that diet can play a role in preventing, managing, and improving:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.Anemia-Care-Instructions.uf8147\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Anemia</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.mayoclinic.org/healthy-lifestyle/adult-health/in-depth/bone-health/art-20045060\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Bone health</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://diabetes.org/healthy-living/recipes-nutrition\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Diabetes</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.heart-healthy-eating.av2065\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Heart disease</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.hsph.harvard.edu/nutritionsource/disease-prevention/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">And more</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nA healthy diet is a powerful medicine. It can add years to your life.'),(3876,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3877,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background',''),(3878,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3879,392,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3880,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3881,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_row-background',''),(3882,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3883,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_row-id',''),(3884,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3885,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_row-class',''),(3886,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3887,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_image','412'),(3888,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(3889,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_url',''),(3890,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_url','field_63ed55a382b95'),(3891,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(3892,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3893,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_headline','Your Prevention Plan'),(3894,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3895,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_text','Staying well by preventing or delaying disease is possible with health screenings and <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.immun#hw254897\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">immunizations</a>. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/learn/preventive-services\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Prevention plans</a> can be tailored to every member of your family.'),(3896,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3897,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_background',''),(3898,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3899,392,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3900,392,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3901,412,'_wp_attached_file','nutrition_feature.jpg'),(3902,412,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(3903,412,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:475;s:6:\"height\";i:320;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"nutrition_feature.jpg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:140501;s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:6:\"medium\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"nutrition_feature-300x202.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:202;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:16086;}s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"nutrition_feature-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:7214;}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(3904,393,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Weight Management'),(3905,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(3906,393,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Eat healthy, move around, and feel better.\r\n\r\nWhatever your reasons for wanting to lose weight, you can find ways to do it that fit your lifestyle and learning style.'),(3907,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(3908,393,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(3909,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(3910,393,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','269'),(3911,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(3912,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background',''),(3913,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3914,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id',''),(3915,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3916,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class',''),(3917,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3918,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','Are You Ready For A Change?'),(3919,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3920,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','Your weight is more than a number on a scale — it \'s how you feel every day, inside and out. Any good plan begins with an assessment.\r\n\r\nStaying at a healthy weight means making small changes that add up to big success:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Please watch this fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_924463.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">A Healthy Weight, Step by Step</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Por favor vea esta fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_924468.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Un peso saludable, paso a paso</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/!ut/p/a0/DcdBCoAgEADAF8naJtp2s_QNlbclpIS0CKnv19wGAswQCj9p45rOwsf_ZY2lxrt_Y9r2ChMECHzXtB4RFomuUx5HQYhGNI2XwmrrBGk9eGodGVRw5Ww_Fw73Gw!!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">how to get started making some changes.</a>'),(3921,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3922,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(3923,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3924,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3925,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3926,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','Resources'),(3927,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3928,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/maryland-virginia-washington-dc/health-wellness/podcasts/live-healthy/weight-loss\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Weight loss meditation and affirmations</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/!ut/p/a0/DcdBCoAgEADAF8mui4h2k_INpTcRMUEtQur7ObcBDwf4Ht6SwyhXD3XexdRHepYvlXwO2MGDD88osSZwGlciksg0KsM4t8gUV3aWzEZCotQC7tbMDyMOIbY!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Calculate your BMI</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/weight-management.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">“Healthy Weight” class</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/15116-plant-based-eating.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Learn about plant-based eating</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Kaiser Permanente <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/healthylifestyles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">online wellness programs</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(3929,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3930,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(3931,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3932,393,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3933,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3934,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background',''),(3935,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3936,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id',''),(3937,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3938,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class',''),(3939,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3940,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','How Can I Help Myself?'),(3941,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3942,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','There are many tools you can use to manage your weight.\r\n\r\nHelp yourself every step of the way:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:weight&amp;article=30B8F7E2-9204-11E0-91CF-9456253626EE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Make food work for you</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:weight&amp;article=FD626AF8-9227-11E0-85EC-EE006BFB88BF\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Stay active</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:weight&amp;article=89206ABA-960E-11E0-B625-9EEF62A65B5F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Overcome challenges</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:weight&amp;article=32B74886-921E-11E0-B3B9-AC0DDA73E57C\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Handle setbacks</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.nationaleatingdisorders.org/20-ways-love-your-body\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Feel good in the body you have</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.sleepfoundation.org/shift-work-disorder/shift-work-you/tips-healthy-eating-and-exercising-when-working-shifts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Follow these tips if you work a shift schedule</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/mh1631e-creating-a-healthy-plate.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">The Plate Method suggests the rights foods and amounts for healthier eating.</a> <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/mh1636sp-creating-a-healthy-plate.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Menus para el plato del buen comer.</a> And check out meal planning for <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"https://higherlogicdownload.s3.amazonaws.com/THEACADEMY/bc90d439-1a0b-4d10-8426-0d0ccc40f516/UploadedImages/DCE/Documents/DCE_Handout_Simplified_Chinese_8th_Revision-1_-_Copy_9-17.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\" type=\"application/pdf\">Chinese</a>, <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"https://higherlogicdownload.s3.amazonaws.com/THEACADEMY/bc90d439-1a0b-4d10-8426-0d0ccc40f516/UploadedImages/DCE/Documents/DCEIndian_best_Final_23Aug18.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\" type=\"application/pdf\">Indian</a>, and <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"https://higherlogicdownload.s3.amazonaws.com/THEACADEMY/bc90d439-1a0b-4d10-8426-0d0ccc40f516/UploadedImages/DCE/Documents/Carb_Counting_-_DCE_Middleeastern_w-logos_English_1Aug19__Academy_approved__.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\" type=\"application/pdf\">Middle Eastern</a> groups.\r\n\r\nHave you visited <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://about.kaiserpermanente.org/total-health/food-for-health\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Food for Health</a>? You\'ll find recipes and short essays about food and nutrition. There are also links to related sites, including these <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLXVDFpw1BnTyPMtzXc3y32R2-rZeXZkiJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">cooking videos</a>.'),(3943,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3944,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(3945,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3946,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3947,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3948,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline',''),(3949,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3950,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Physical activity is an important part of managing your weight. This guide for older adults contains <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.nia.nih.gov/health/publication/exercise-physical-activity/introduction\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">lots of good information for people of all ages</a>.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/static/health/pdfs/nutrition/nat_food_and_activity_diary_nutrition.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Keep track of your food</a>, water, exercise, sleep, and more. It can help you see patterns and make better choices.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.myfitnesspal.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Try MyFitnessPal</a> or other app. Learn more about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/!ut/p/a0/FchBDoMgEADAt_iAzerWoPRGC29o4bYhGyQRNITU77c9zmDAN4bKn5y456Py_rOPUru0-yU5bR1fGDCcjVNh9PWAyHGT_3HrOe6CfiS7zo6eoIkWmCY3glHGglbq4fTN6oVmPEtZLzMMX5ReQlI!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">how to get and stay on track</a>.\r\n\r\nUse a <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/17850-personal-action-plan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">personal action plan</a> to help you reach your goals.\r\n\r\nIf you are a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, check out <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.smartpatients.com/communities/weight\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Smart Patients</a>. We are helping create a new online community to make it easier for people concerned about weight management to learn from each other. At the same time, you’ll help Kaiser Permanente  learn more about the questions and topics that matter most to you.'),(3951,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3952,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(3953,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3954,393,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3955,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3956,393,'wellness_layout_topic','a:7:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";i:6;s:3:\"row\";}'),(3957,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background',''),(3958,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3959,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','video'),(3960,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3961,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class',''),(3962,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3963,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fqhYBTg73fw&t=216s'),(3964,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','field_6402c9c746e19'),(3965,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-video\";}'),(3966,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3967,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','The Best Diet Is Healthy Eating'),(3968,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3969,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','This 15-minute video has great ideas about scientifically-supported ways to lose weight and improve your health. Explore options for healthy lifestyle changes by watching this video to learn more. You can call a <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coach</a> to get  support for the changes you’re interested in making and/or maintaining.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fqhYBTg73fw&amp;t=216s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Watch this video to learn more</a>.'),(3970,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3971,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(3972,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3973,393,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3974,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3975,165,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(3976,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(3977,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(3978,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id',''),(3979,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(3980,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(3981,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(3982,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Plant-Based Eating'),(3983,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(3984,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','Plant-based diets are based on minimally processed vegetables, tubers, whole grains, legumes, fruits, nuts, and seeds. Research has shown there are many health benefits to eating all or mostly plant foods.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/NF-103-plant-based-diets.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Types of plant-based diets</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/NF-104-plant.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Books and other resources</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/15116-plant-based-eating.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">“Plant-based Eating” booklet</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn more in “Plant-based Eating Program,” a 3-week series taught by a registered dietitian. Kaiser Permanente Northwest members can take this class online. <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/plant-based-eating-ppt-for-website.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Review the class presentation</a>. To register, call 503-286-6816 or 1-866-301-3866 and select option 2.'),(3985,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(3986,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(3987,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(3988,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3989,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(3990,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','How Do I Get My Family Involved?'),(3991,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(3992,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','Helping your family towards a healthy lifestyle is easier than you think.\r\n\r\nInformation to help you:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://members.kaiserpermanente.org/redirects/landingpages/afd/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Amazing Food Detective</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=content:health-encyclopedia&amp;hwid=ud3719\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Find new ways to add in fruits and veggies</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.hopkinsallchildrens.org/Patients-Families/Health-Library/HealthDocNew/Healthy-Drinks-for-Kids/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Choose healthy drinks</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/Healthy-Weight.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Follow the 5-2-1-0 rule</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn more about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/!ut/p/a0/FchRCoQgEADQs3SAYTJNdP8M6gq7-jfIYEJaiNT1d_fzPQz4wVDpzol6PisdP_vItXN7PZzT3vGNAcPVKBVCX0-IFHf-H7We48HonZrV6JYV9GYkCLGOYKU0YPUirZonsU0ar1LM44bhC_s_29E!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">keeping your family healthy</a>.'),(3993,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(3994,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(3995,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(3996,393,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(3997,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(3998,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-background',''),(3999,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4000,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-id',''),(4001,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4002,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-class',''),(4003,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4004,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(4005,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4006,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','We can all use a little help as we’re working towards a goal. As you work to get to and maintain a healthy weight, a health coach can be a valuable resource in your journey. A coach can help you figure out your patterns and behaviors, set goals, and find new coping strategies.\r\n\r\nLearn more about Kaiser Permanente’s <a href=\"https://healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching sessions</a>.'),(4007,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4008,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(4009,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4010,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4011,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4012,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','Your Total Health'),(4013,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4014,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','Sometimes, you might find yourself caring for and prioritizing the health of your loved ones ahead of your own health. Try these tools and strategies to <a href=\"https://www.powerfultoolsforcaregivers.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">better handle caregiving challenges you might face.</a>\r\n\r\nRemember, your well-being is affected by both your mind and your body. It\'s important to take good care of each to have complete health. Learn how to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/!ut/p/a0/Dcc7DoAgDADQ0zhqnd08hcJCKlQgfFOribfX6eWBhh10xSd6lNgq5v_KUhXipfxgHgNhlgAbaNCpmys0FnuLYTqJmRhU6lNjP8wlVnc090IvZf0A9Gg4cw!!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for the whole you</a>.'),(4015,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4016,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(4017,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4018,393,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4019,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4020,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background',''),(4021,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4022,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id',''),(4023,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4024,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class',''),(4025,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4026,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_image','165'),(4027,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(4028,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_url',''),(4029,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_url','field_63ed55a382b95'),(4030,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(4031,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4032,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','Your Prevention Plan'),(4033,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4034,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','Staying well by preventing or delaying disease is possible with kids’ health screenings and immunizations. Prevention plans can be tailored to every member of your family.\r\n\r\nLearn more about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/!ut/p/a0/04_Sj9CPykssy0xPLMnMz0vMAfIjk1PzSlKLrAqKUsuALKCwfkG2oyIAiahodw!!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">preventive care services</a>.'),(4035,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4036,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background',''),(4037,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4038,393,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4039,393,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4040,397,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Kids and Family Health'),(4041,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(4042,397,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Do it for you. And them.\r\n\r\nYou want what’s best for your family. You especially want to make sure your kids thrive.'),(4043,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(4044,397,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(4045,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(4046,197,'_genesis_title','Kids & Family Health'),(4047,197,'_genesis_description','Help your kids & family thrive by utilizing these great resources! From healthy habits to health coaching, you\'ll find the information you\'re looking for.'),(4048,197,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4049,397,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','197'),(4050,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(4051,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background',''),(4052,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4053,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id',''),(4054,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4055,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class',''),(4056,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4057,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','Coping With COVID-19'),(4058,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4059,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','Families are navigating lots of new territory during the COVID-19 pandemic — remote learning, maintaining connections when you can’t socialize or play with friends in person, supporting emotional stability, and more.\r\n\r\nCheck these family resources for tips and tools:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.mghclaycenter.org/hot-topics/7-ways-to-support-kids-and-teens-through-the-coronavirus-pandemic/?fbclid=IwAR3HdJs2lZjKEY8g0I25hk374sYUeLMbqzXw3kHmb4v51kT-c6KSAx6TQ3Y\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">The Clay Center for Healthy Young Minds: 7 ways to support kids and teens through the pandemic</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://home.mcleanhospital.org/webinar-series\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">McLean Hospital: Free webinars on child and teen mental health, parenting burnout, sleep, and more</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.massgeneral.org/faculty-development/offices/owb/covid19-resources-for-parents\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Mass General Office for Wellbeing: COVID-19 resources for parents</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/17/parenting/coronavirus-kids-talk.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">The New York Times: How to talk to kids about coronavirus</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4060,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4061,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(4062,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4063,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4064,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4065,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','5-2-1-0'),(4066,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4067,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','Start your children on a healthier track with 5-2-1-0 (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/17771-5-2-1-0-flyer.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">English</a>, <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/17771A-Spanish-5-2-1-0.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Espanol</a>).\r\n\r\nEvery day, work towards:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.healthychildren.org/English/healthy-living/nutrition/Pages/How-to-Get-Your-Child-to-Eat-More-Fruits-and-Veggies.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">5 or more fruits and veggies</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.media-and-your-child-making-choices.abx2677\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">2 hours or less of screen time</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/physicalactivity/basics/children/index.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">1 hour or more of physical activity</a></li>\r\n 	<li>0 sugar-sweetened drinks (<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/TR9vUvmExQr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">English video</a>, <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/8ySMAo5KaQQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Espanol video</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(4068,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4069,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(4070,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4071,397,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4072,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4073,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background',''),(4074,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4075,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id',''),(4076,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4077,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class',''),(4078,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4079,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','Help Your Child Learn Good Habits'),(4080,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4081,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','Here\'s a short tip sheet of <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/10-healthy-habits.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">10 Healthy Habits</a>, in English and Espanol.\r\n\r\nTry using <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/Images/CheckMyHabitsForFamilies_tcm75-1506014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">this worksheet</a> to identify changes your family might be ready for now. Consider experimenting with just 1 or 2 changes at a time.\r\n\r\nWrite down goals and action steps for yourself and <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/healthy-goal-setting-for-parents_tcm28-203380.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">keep track of how often you reach them</a>.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://thrive.kaiserpermanente.org/care-near-you/northern-california/gsaa/wp-content/uploads/sites/18/2015/11/Healthy-Goal-Setting-for-Kids_tcm28-203378.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Your children can do it, too!</a>\r\n\r\nSometimes, you might need a little help keeping your family on track with their health and wellness goals. A health coach can provide support and information as you work toward goals, and help you find new coping strategies and stay on course. Learn more about Kaiser Permanente\'s <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching</a>.'),(4082,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4083,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(4084,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4085,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4086,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4087,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','Raising Active Kids'),(4088,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4089,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Being active helps you be healthier and stronger — and feel your best — at every age.\r\n\r\nWant your family to be more active together?\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>In Portland, play in the streets during <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.portland.gov/sunday-parkways\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Sunday Parkways presented by Kaiser Permanente</a>, a series of free events opening the city\'s largest public space - its streets - to walk, bike, roll, and play.</li>\r\n 	<li>Write down different activities on slips of paper and keep them in a “Get Up and Move” jar you can go to for ideas.</li>\r\n 	<li>Check your area park and recreation districts for activities and events.</li>\r\n 	<li>Try <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.gonoodle.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">GoNoodle</a> for lots of fun, short activities.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEncourage your kids\' schools to make physical activity a priority. Thriving Schools has <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://thrivingschools.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-resources/physical-activity/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">some good tips and resources</a>.'),(4090,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4091,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(4092,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4093,397,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4094,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4095,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background',''),(4096,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4097,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','video'),(4098,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4099,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class',''),(4100,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4101,182,'_genesis_title','Kids & Family Health'),(4102,182,'_genesis_description','Help your kids & family thrive by utilizing these great resources! From healthy habits to health coaching, you\'ll find the information you\'re looking for.'),(4103,182,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4104,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','182'),(4105,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(4106,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:32:\"Learning Module: Healthy Futures\";s:3:\"url\";s:83:\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/learning-module-healthy-futures/\";s:6:\"target\";s:0:\"\";}'),(4107,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','field_63ed55a382b95'),(4108,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(4109,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4110,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','Healthy Futures'),(4111,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4112,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','Take conflict off the menu. Learn proven strategies for coping with difficult eaters in the “Healthy Futures” webinar. You\'ll also learn how to make mealtime more pleasant and rewarding for your family.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/learning-module-healthy-futures/\">Watch a recorded presentation now.</a>\r\n\r\nHealth coaches can support your and your family\'s wellness. Talk with them about <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pv-021-healthy-futures-family-coaching.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">coaching for your family.</a>'),(4113,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4114,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(4115,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4116,397,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4117,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4118,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(4119,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4120,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id',''),(4121,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4122,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(4123,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4124,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Encouraging Smart Food Choices'),(4125,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4126,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','Good nutrition is fundamental to healthy living.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.myplate.gov/life-stages/families\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">Find an eating style that works for your family and fits your everyday life</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Check out this webinar and related resources on overweight children and <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.ellynsatterinstitute.org/education/webinars-2/webinar-child-overweight-helping-without-harming/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">“Helping Without Harming.”</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.feeding-your-child-using-division-of-responsibility.ug2200?kpSearch=Divisions%20of%20Responsibility\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Help your family with who-when-how much of eating</a> with the Divisions of Responsibility.</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://thrivingschools.kaiserpermanente.org/students/healthy-eating/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Promote healthy eating at your kids\' schools</a> with these tips and strategies from Thriving Schools.</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://about.kaiserpermanente.org/total-health/food-for-health\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Food for Health</a> has recipes and short essays about food and nutrition. There are also links to related sites, including these <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLXVDFpw1BnTyPMtzXc3y32R2-rZeXZkiJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">cooking videos</a>, some featuring child helpers/testers.</li>\r\n 	<li>Being a picky eater is common among young children. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.myplate.gov/life-stages/preschoolers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">These tips can help you deal with it in a positive way</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(4127,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4128,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(4129,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4130,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4131,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4132,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','Watch These Fotonovelas For Health Tips'),(4133,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4134,397,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','Please watch these fotonovelas:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_812894.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Be Smart, Turn the TV Off</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_812897.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Family Fun Brings Us Together</a></li>\r\n 	