78b5'),(4148,397,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','Helping your child through the tween and teenage years can be a daunting task. They\'re growing up, their bodies are changing, and they\'re more emotional about what you may consider to be the smallest things.\r\n\r\nLearn more about how to guide your <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.growth-and-development-ages-11-to-14-years.te7233\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">tween (11-14)</a> and <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.te7221\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">teen (15-18)</a> to a healthy lifestyle.\r\n\r\nSome good resources for your kids include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://teenshealth.org/en/teens/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">teenshealth.org</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.sutterhealth.org/pamf/health/teens/female/puberty-changes-females\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Puberty–females</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.girlshealth.gov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">girlshealth.gov</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.sutterhealth.org/pamf/health/teens/male/puberty-changes-males\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Puberty–males</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://medlineplus.gov/teenhealth.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">MedlinePlus: Teen Health</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.plannedparenthood.org/learn/teens\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Planned Parenthood: Teen Wire</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4149,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4150,397,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(4151,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4152,397,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4153,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4154,196,'_genesis_title','Kids & Family Health'),(4155,196,'_genesis_description','Help your kids & family thrive by utilizing these great resources! From healthy habits to health coaching, you\'ll find the information you\'re looking for.'),(4156,196,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4157,397,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_image','196'),(4158,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_image','field_63edb16465fe1'),(4159,397,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_url',''),(4160,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_url','field_63edb17765fe2'),(4161,397,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(4162,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4163,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background',''),(4164,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4165,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id',''),(4166,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4167,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class',''),(4168,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4169,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','Keeping Baby Healthy'),(4170,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4171,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','Helping your newborn have the best start in life is essential. From <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/baby-101/breastfeeding\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">breastfeeding</a> and bathing to how to calm your newborn, ensuring best total health from day one is critical.\r\n\r\nIf you are a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/lookbook.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">choose a doctor for your baby.</a>\r\n\r\nLearn more about how to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/baby-101\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for your newborn</a> and <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/labor-delivery/recovery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for yourself</a>.\r\n\r\nWhen your baby sends signals that she\'s hungry or full, it\'s important to respond promptly — and in a way that\'s warm and loving. This is called “responsive feeding” — <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o6dO3W-SJK0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">watch a video</a> or <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.healthychildren.org/English/ages-stages/baby/feeding-nutrition/Pages/Is-Your-Baby-Hungry-or-Full-Responsive-Feeding-Explained.aspx?_ga=2.137642615.636105204.1655741212-1464897864.1655741211&amp;_gl=1*1dir55a*_ga*MTQ2NDg5Nzg2NC4xNjU1NzQxMjEx*_ga_FD9D3XZVQQ*MTY1NTc0MTIxMS4xLjEuMTY1NTc0MTIzOS4w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">read about it</a>. When your child is a little older, <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l-n-dvAfpDQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">watch this video for tips about infant feeding </a>and introducing solid foods. You can also read these <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.healthychildren.org/English/ages-stages/baby/feeding-nutrition/Pages/Starting-Solid-Foods.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">tips for starting solids.</a>'),(4172,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4173,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background',''),(4174,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4175,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4176,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4177,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','Your Prevention Plan'),(4178,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4179,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','Staying well by preventing or delaying disease is possible with kids’ health screenings and immunizations. Prevention plans can be tailored to every member of your family.\r\n\r\nLearn more about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/washington/health-wellness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">preventive care and wellness resources</a>.\r\n\r\nKaiser Permanente members can sign up to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/secure/profile/act-for-a-family-member#/dashboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Act for a Family Member</a> — order prescriptions, send email, and view lab results and other health info of a family member.'),(4180,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4181,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background',''),(4182,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4183,397,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4184,397,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4185,397,'wellness_layout_topic','a:7:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";i:6;s:3:\"row\";}'),(4190,192,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4191,223,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4192,389,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Pain'),(4193,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(4194,389,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Take charge of your health.\r\n\r\nTaking an active role in your health can help you feel better — and become better equipped to deal with life’s ups and downs. Learn different strategies to manage your pain and improve your ability to function.'),(4195,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(4196,389,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(4197,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(4198,221,'_genesis_title','Chronic Pain Management Resources'),(4199,221,'_genesis_description','What are the causes of chronic pain & how can this type of pain be managed? Kaiser Permanente Health & Wellness Services offers resources, coping methods & more.'),(4200,221,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4201,389,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','221'),(4202,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(4203,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background',''),(4204,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4205,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id',''),(4206,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4207,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class',''),(4208,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4209,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','What’s The Difference Between Acute And Chronic Pain?'),(4210,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4211,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','Pain usually starts when nerves send signals to your brain, telling it you have an injury or illness.\r\n\r\nAcute pain doesn\'t last long. It may result from an injury or illness.\r\n\r\nWith chronic pain, your body might heal but your brain keeps getting “pain signals.” The pain becomes persistent. Chronic pain is often “invisible.” You might look healthy to others, while still suffering from extreme pain.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C_3phB93rvI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Watch this video about the brain-pain connection</a>, and how to tackle chronic pain.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.cpain#tr2757\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-192\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/hqdefault-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" /></a>'),(4212,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4213,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(4214,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4215,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4216,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4217,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','What Happens When You Feel Pain?'),(4218,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4219,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','Pain signals from the body do not go to a single location in the brain. Instead, they go to several different networks of brain cells. The networks work together to determine how you experience the pain.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pain-page-brain-graphic-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"354\" height=\"362\" />\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Attention:</strong> Controls how much attention you direct toward and away from pain.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Sensory:</strong> Processes the location and intensity of pain and whether pain is sharp, dull, or burning.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Action:</strong> allows you to respond to pain with your behavior.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Feelings/motivation:</strong> Influences how unpleasant and threatening pain is by processing related thoughts, feelings (fear, anger, depression), and stress responses.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Pain control:</strong> Takes messages from the other brain networks and controls your experience of pain by producing natural painkillers called endorphins. This network sends signals from the brain down into the spinal cord and out to the body.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(4220,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4221,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background',''),(4222,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4223,389,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4224,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4225,389,'wellness_layout_topic','a:6:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";}'),(4226,191,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4227,222,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4228,224,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4229,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background',''),(4230,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4231,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id',''),(4232,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4233,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class',''),(4234,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4235,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','How Can I Help Myself?'),(4236,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4237,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','You can help yourself with chronic pain. Start by listening to your body!\r\n\r\nA few things to try include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.improving-sleep-when-you-have-chronic-pain.hw195941\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Getting enough sleep</a><strong>\r\n</strong></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.stress-management-breathing-exercises-for-relaxation.uz2255?kpSearch=deep%20breathing%20relaxation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Deep breathing</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.healthline.com/health/exercises-to-reduce-chronic-pain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Exercising</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Getting encouragement and tools with <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/healthylifestyles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">online wellness programs</a> that help you create positive changes in your life</li>\r\n 	<li>Following all <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.chronic-pain-care-instructions.uh3660\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care instructions</a> from your person doctor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKaiser Permanente members have access to digital mental health and wellness tools at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check out this page</a> the Calm, Ginger, or myStrength apps. You also can<a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\"> call a health coach</a> for 6-month subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.'),(4238,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4239,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(4240,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4241,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4242,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4243,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','Stop And Breathe'),(4244,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4245,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Whenever you feel like you need to catch your breath, <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5DqTuWve9t8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">do this 30-second breathing exercise</a> for instant relaxation.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5DqTuWve9t8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/hqdefault.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" /></a>'),(4246,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4247,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(4248,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4249,389,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4250,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4251,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background',''),(4252,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4253,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id',''),(4254,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4255,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class',''),(4256,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4257,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_headline','Activity-Rest Cycle'),(4258,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4259,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_text','Being active is important. It can be an effective way to manage pain. One thing that is even more important is how you balance activity with rest. Check out these two models that describe what this can look like\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pain-page-activity-cycle.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"379\" />\r\n\r\nYou might sometimes find yourself overdoing activities to “catch up” after periods of restricted activity. This can result in severe pain, which then may force you to rest for even longer periods, creating a pain overactivity cycle.'),(4260,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4261,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_background',''),(4262,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4263,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4264,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4265,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline',''),(4266,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4267,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','The activity-rest cycle is a better way to increase the amount of activity you can do over time.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pain-page-rest-cycle.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"369\" height=\"371\" />\r\n\r\nTo use this cycle, first identify an activity you tend to overdo. Then decide how long you can do the activity before you need to stop, rest, relax, and restart.'),(4268,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4269,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(4270,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4271,389,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4272,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4273,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(4274,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4275,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id',''),(4276,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4277,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(4278,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4279,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Common Chronic Pain Conditions'),(4280,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4281,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','While the cause of chronic pain can vary, there are some common pain conditions. Learn more about each:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.osteoarthritis.hw125723\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Arthritis and joint pain</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.fibromyalgia.hw196365\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Fibromyalgia</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.back-and-neck-pain.center1002\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Back pain</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.headaches.center1019\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Headaches</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.chronic-female-pelvic-pain.tv2262?kpSearch=chronic%20pelvic%20pain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Chronic pelvic pain</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.groin-pain.sig46230spec\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Groin pain</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.neuropathic-pain-care-instructions.ut2299\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Nerve pain (neuropathy)</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCheck out these videos on symptoms, treatment, and prevention of:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rtdIVk1TaxY&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Back pain</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8t8DAh83gkI&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;list=PLXcU9ozQ2WFy3_zHvXiufXv9Rb--SCXYJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Heel pain</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EPDqf9QSW1o&amp;list=PLXcU9ozQ2WFykvc2MnnphdaUoHqKNkm12&amp;index=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Knee pain</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDxYoasawkE&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;list=PLXcU9ozQ2WFxn0sB89gjGuPL16HjjrYNe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Shoulder pain</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4282,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4283,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(4284,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4285,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4286,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4287,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(4288,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4289,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','Sometimes, we all need a little help as we\'re dealing with health conditions. As you work to manage chronic pain, a health coach can help you work towards your goals, find new coping strategies, and keep on track.\r\n\r\nLearn more about Kaiser Permanente\'s <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching</a> sessions.\r\n<h2>Your Total Health</h2>\r\nRemember, your well-being is affected by both your mind and your body. It\'s important to take good care of both to have complete health.\r\n\r\nLearn how to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.mind-body-wellness.mente\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for the whole you</a>.'),(4290,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4291,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(4292,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4293,389,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4294,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4295,220,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4296,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-background',''),(4297,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4298,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-id',''),(4299,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4300,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-class',''),(4301,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4302,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','Can Pain Cause Depression?'),(4303,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4304,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','It’s not unusual for mental health problems to occur with long-term physical problems. Chronic pain sufferers often feel isolated by their conditions, which can lead to depression. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.depression-anxiety-and-physical-health-problems.ug5079\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Learn more about this topic</a>.\r\n<h2>Making A Plan</h2>\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.learning-about-making-a-plan-for-managing-chronic-pain.aci4968\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">A pain management plan</a> can help relieve symptoms. It can include medication, massage, counseling, tai chi … whatever you find helps.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.work-closely-with-your-doctor.prtnr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Work with your personal doctor</a> on your plan. A doctor who not only knows your medical history but understands what\'s important to you may be the resource you need most.'),(4305,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4306,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(4307,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4308,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4309,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4310,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','Looking For More?'),(4311,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4312,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','If you’re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, you can discuss treatment needs or set up an appointment by calling the Kaiser Permanente Mental Health Department, 503-249-3434 or 1-855-632-8280.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-220\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pain_feature.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"300\" />'),(4313,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4314,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(4315,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4316,389,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4317,389,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4318,394,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Prediabetes'),(4319,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(4320,394,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Good health is awareness.\r\n\r\nWhat is prediabetes? What’s an A1c of 5.7 or higher mean? Learn more — and about how lifestyle changes can make a difference to your health.'),(4321,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(4322,394,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(4323,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(4324,156,'_genesis_title','Prediabetes Information & Resources'),(4325,156,'_genesis_description','Learn more about prediabetes & access online resources & tools to educate yourself on this condition. Get prevention tips & more from the experts!'),(4326,156,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4327,394,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','156'),(4328,3