e','Your Total Health'),(4466,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4467,394,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_text','Remember, your well-being is affected by both your mind and your body. It\'s important to take good care of each to have complete health.\r\n\r\nLearn how to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for the whole you.</a>'),(4468,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4469,394,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_background',''),(4470,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4471,394,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4472,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4473,394,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_headline','Talk To A Health Coach About Your Options'),(4474,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4475,394,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_text','Sometimes, we all need a little help as we\'re working towards a goal. As you work to stay healthy and prevent diabetes, a health coach can help you explore your options and offer support to stay on track and reach your goals.\r\n\r\nLearn more about Kaiser Permanente\'s <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching</a> sessions.'),(4476,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4477,394,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_background',''),(4478,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4479,394,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4480,394,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4481,394,'wellness_layout_topic','a:8:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"