days</a>.\r\n\r\nYou can also optimize your health before you get pregnant. Consider a class or health coaching to quit tobacco, lose weight, or manage diabetes. <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/classes/\">Check the <em>Healthy Living</em> catalog.</a>'),(4502,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4503,395,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(4504,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4505,395,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4506,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4507,395,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','I Just Found Out I\'m Pregnant! Now What?'),(4508,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4509,395,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','You\'re about to start a wonderful journey. And you\'re likely to have lots of questions along the way. Questions like:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>How your body is changing</li>\r\n 	<li>Your developing baby</li>\r\n 	<li>Options during labor</li>\r\n 	<li>How to get ready for birth</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://totalhealthvideos.kaiserpermanente.org/maternity/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">A library of more than 100 pregnancy and childbirth videos is available to answer your questions.</a>'),(4510,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4511,395,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(4512,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4513,395,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4514,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4515,395,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background',''),(4516,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4517,395,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id',''),(4518,395,'