ic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4529,395,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(4530,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4531,395,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4532,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4533,395,'wellness_layout_topic','a:9:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";i:6;s:3:\"row\";i:7;s:3:\"row\";i:8;s:3:\"row\";}'),(4534,230,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4535,75,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4536,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background',''),(4537,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4538,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','video'),(4539,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4540,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class',''),(4541,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4548,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-video\";}'),(4549,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4550,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','During: How Can I Have A Healthy Pregnancy'),(4551,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4552,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','Most women expect to gain some weight during pregnancy. But too much can cause problems. These include gestational diabetes, a larger baby, or delivery complications.\r\n\r\nWatch this video for info about what you should eat, how much weight you should gain, and if and how you should exercise while pregnant.\r\n\r\nIf you’re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, you can join the free Healthy Pregnancy program. You’ll get help setting and achieving your diet, exercise, and weight gain goals during pregnancy.\r\n\r\nThese resources offer helpful info:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/healthypregnancy-compilation-ada.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Healthy Pregnancy guidelines</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/15089-healthy-pregnancy-plate-ada.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Healthy pregnancy plate</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/healthy_plate_lat_sp.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">El plato saludable, dieta latina</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4553,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4554,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(4555,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4556,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4557,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4558,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(4559,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4560,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id',''),(4561,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4562,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(4563,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4564,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Gestational Diabetes'),(4565,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4566,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','Some women develop <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/gestational-diabetes/\">gestational diabetes</a> while pregnant. But with treatment, most women who have it are able to control their blood sugar and give birth to healthy babies.\r\n\r\nLearn about:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.gestational-diabetes.hw197466?kpSearch=gestational%20diabetes#hw197574\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Diagnosing gestational diabetes</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/14665-hypoglycemia-for-pregnancy-page.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Low blood sugar (hypoglycemia) during pregnancy</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.gestational-diabetes.hw197466?kpSearch=gestational%20diabetes#hw197665\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Home treatment </a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/18124-gdm-healthy-eating-during-pregnancy.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Healthy eating during pregnancy</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/diabetes/overview/preventing-type-2-diabetes/game-plan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">It’s never too early to prevent diabetes</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-230\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pregnancy_feature2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"265\" />'),(4567,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4568,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(4569,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4570,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4571,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4572,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','How Do I Plan For Childbirth?'),(4573,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4574,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','Every pregnant person\'s experience of labor and delivery is different. But there are a few simple steps every person can take to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/labor-delivery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">prepare for this life-changing experience</a>. Understanding the process and being as prepared as possible will help you feel more relaxed and in control.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Plan <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/content/dam/kporg/maternity/pdf/what-to-bring-to-hospital.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">what to bring to the hospital</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Explore <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.labor-and-delivery.tn9759?kpSearch=labor%20and%20delivery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">labor and delivery info</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Review <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/third-trimester/baby-items\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">new baby essentials</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.interactive-tool-what-is-your-due-date.tn9888?kpSearch=interactive%20tool%20due%20date\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Interactive tool: What is your due date?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you’re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, you can also:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Take a <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pregnancy-childbirth-and-newborn-care.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Preparation for Birth class</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Complete a <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/15837ob_questionnaire.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">prenatal questionnaire</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Create a <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/fillable_birthpreferencesplan.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">birth preferences plan</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Choose a doctor for your baby — <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/look-book-eugene.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Eugene</a> and <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/lookbook.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Portland area</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Review the “Baby on the Way” book you were given at your first appointment. It’s also <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/19433-baby-on-the-way.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">available online</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn more about Kaiser Permanente’s prenatal commitment to you and t<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/maternity/expect-great-care\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">he support you will receive from our expert staff</a>.'),(4575,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4576,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(4577,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4578,395,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4579,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4580,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-background',''),(4581,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4582,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-id',''),(4583,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4584,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-class',''),(4585,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4586,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','Birth Tours And Maternity Care'),(4587,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4588,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/18691_childbirth_tour_ada.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">A hospital birth tour</a> provides information about your birth experience, from admission to discharge. You will also have the opportunity to see your hospital’s labor, birthing, and family rooms.<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\nIf you are a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, get details for a tour at:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pregnancy-childbirth-and-newborn-care.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Kaiser Permanente Sunnyside and Westside medical centers</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.legacyhealth.org/Services-and-Resources/services/adult/womens-services/maternity-care/having-your-baby/classes-pregnancy-and-parenting-education\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Legacy Salmon Creek Medical Center</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://salemhealth.org/services/family-birth-center\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Salem Hospital Family Birth Center</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou can take a tour in person or online. For online, check out the <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/sunnyside-birth-tour-webinar-ada.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Sunnyside</a> and <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/westside-tour-webinar-ada.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Westside</a> presentations.\r\n\r\nLearn more about maternity care – including where to go for care, what to expect on your delivery day, and information for family and friends – at:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/find-hospital/sunnyside\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">kp.org/maternity/sunnyside</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/find-hospital/westside\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">kp.org/maternity/westside</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/find-hospital/salem-health\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">kp.org/maternity/salem</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/find-hospital/salmon-creek\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">kp.org/maternity/salmoncreek</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4589,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4590,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(4591,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4592,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4593,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4594,229,'_genesis_title','Pregnancy & Childbirth Resources'),(4595,229,'_genesis_description','There are so many questions to consider during pregnancy & childbirth that it can feel overwhelming. Access these links to valuable & trusted resources.'),(4596,229,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4597,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_image','229'),(4598,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_image','field_63edb16465fe1'),(4599,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_url',''),(4600,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_url','field_63edb17765fe2'),(4601,395,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(4602,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4603,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background',''),(4604,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4605,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id',''),(4606,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4607,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class',''),(4608,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4609,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','What If I Have Other Questions?'),(4610,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4611,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Pregnancy overview</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:pregnancy&amp;article=86368466-B223-11E0-BDEA-C899CC27A35E\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Health and safety</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:pregnancy&amp;article=54C03D34-B19A-11E0-B96E-CDB82066CA6E\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Symptoms and discomforts</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:pregnancy&amp;article=5082BF3A-B19A-11E0-98D8-D26C2F741FE7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Problems or complications</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/16076_early-pregnancy-bleeding.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Bleeding or pain during early pregnancy</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/poc?uri=center:pregnancy&amp;article=DA135914-BD41-11E0-A839-D0776BA04C72\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Twins or more</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4612,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4613,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background',''),(4614,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4615,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4616,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4617,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','What Can I Expect During Labor And Delivery?'),(4618,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4619,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','Giving birth is a scary, exciting, and thrilling experience. Being prepared is the key to having a good experience.\r\n\r\nLearn about labor and delivery, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.tn9759#tp22259\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Signs of labor </a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.tn8162#tn8163\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">C-section (cesarean section)</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.vaginal-birth-after-cesarean-vbac.hw200557?kpSearch=vaginal%20birth%20after%20cesarean\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Vaginal birth after cesarean (VBAC)</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.abl1277#abl1278\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Postpartum: First 6 weeks after childbirth</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhile every labor and delivery is different, they all have three stages. Learn more about the <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.labor-and-delivery.tn9759?kpSearch=postpartum%20the%20first%206%20weeks#tn9815\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">3 stages of labor and delivery</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you’re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, get to know your:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Labor and Delivery Care Team — <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/labor-and-delivery-eugene-look-book.pdf\" type=\"application/pdf\">Eugene</a> and <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/labor-and-delivery-portland-area-look-book.pdf\" type=\"application/pdf\">Portland area</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Baby’s Nursery Care Team — <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/13564-nursery-clinicians-portland-area-look-book.pdf\" type=\"application/pdf\">Portland area</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4620,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4621,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background',''),(4622,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4623,395,'wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4624,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_6_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4625,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_row-background',''),(4626,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4627,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_row-id',''),(4628,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4629,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_row-class',''),(4630,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4631,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_headline','After: Caring For Your Baby'),(4632,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4633,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_text','Once your baby is born, take time to enjoy and savor every beautiful moment.\r\n\r\nYou may feel a little anxious about caring for your newborn. You may want to:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/video/caring-for-your-newborn-video-1600408\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Watch videos on the basics of newborn care</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/ncbddd/hearingloss/parentsguide/understanding/newbornhearingscreening.html#:~:text=Infants%20and%20Babies\'%20Hearing%20Can%20Be%20Checked&amp;text=A%20baby\'s%20hearing%20can%20be,or%20in%20their%20mothers\'%20room.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Understand the newborn hearing screening process</a>.</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ve7yXXRaYT8&amp;t=9s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Watch a video about newborn cues–what your baby is trying to communicate.</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Learn more about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.postpartum-first-6-weeks-after-childbirth.abl1277?kpSearch=postpartum\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">the postpartum period</a> and how to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/baby-101\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for your baby</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen your baby sends signals that she’s hungry or full, it’s important to respond promptly — and in a way that’s warm and loving. This is called “responsive feeding” — <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o6dO3W-SJK0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">watch a video</a> or <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.healthychildren.org/English/ages-stages/baby/feeding-nutrition/Pages/Is-Your-Baby-Hungry-or-Full-Responsive-Feeding-Explained.aspx?_ga=2.65207725.2077690263.1672343522-777898025.1672343521&amp;_gl=1*yv9kbm*_ga*Nzc3ODk4MDI1LjE2NzIzNDM1MjE.*_ga_FD9D3XZVQQ*MTY3MjM0MzUyMS4xLjEuMTY3MjM0MzU0Mi4wLjAuMA..\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">read a handout</a> about it. When your child is a little older, <a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l-n-dvAfpDQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">watch this video about infant feeding </a>and introducing solid foods. You can also read these <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.healthychildren.org/English/ages-stages/baby/feeding-nutrition/Pages/Tips-for-Introducing-Solid-Foods.aspx?_gl=1*2mr72u*_ga*Nzc3ODk4MDI1LjE2NzIzNDM1MjE.*_ga_FD9D3XZVQQ*MTY3MjM0MzUyMS4xLjEuMTY3MjM0MzYyMi4wLjAuMA..&amp;_ga=2.124507657.2077690263.1672343522-777898025.1672343521\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">tips for introducing solids</a>.\r\n\r\nKaiser Permanente Northwest members can also:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Take the helpful “Tool Kit for New Parents” class. <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/240399_ada-tool-kit-for-new-parents.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">You can view the booklet here.</a></li>\r\n 	<li>After pregnancy and birth, learn about things you can do to address some changes to your body, such as posture, bowel changes, and back pain. Female Kaiser Permanente Northwest members can take a free webinar, “My Body After Baby.” To register, call 1-844-394-3972.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(4634,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4635,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_background',''),(4636,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4637,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4638,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4639,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_headline','What Should I Know About Breastfeeding, And Breast Health After My Baby Is Born?'),(4640,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4641,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_text','Your breasts will go through many changes throughout pregnancy, and well after labor and delivery. Learn more:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.breastfeeding.hw91687?kpSearch=breastfeeding\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Breastfeeding</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.breast-engorgement.hw133953?kpSearch=breast%20engorgement\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Breast engorgement</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.mastitis-while-breastfeeding.hw98039?kpSearch=mastitis%20breastfeeding\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Mastitis while breastfeeding</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.thrush.hw139068?kpSearch=thrush%20breastfeeding\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Thrush</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.weaning.hw97699?kpSearch=weaning%20breastfeeding\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Weaning</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThere are <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/Proper-Nutrition-While-Breastfeeding.pdf\" rel=\"\">a few guidelines </a> that can help you get the nutrition your body and your baby need while you’re breastfeeding.\r\n\r\nIf you’re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, you can attend <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/pregnancy-childbirth-and-newborn-care.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">prenatal and postpartum breastfeeding support groups</a>.\r\n\r\nRemember to take care of yourself by having a healthy lifestyle and getting all recommended health screenings, including a <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/19032-breast-cancer-faq.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">mammogram to screen for breast cancer </a>(information in English, Spanish, and Russian).\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-75\" src=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/2011-kp-9838.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"360\" />'),(4642,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4643,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_background',''),(4644,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4645,395,'wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4646,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_7_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4647,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_row-background',''),(4648,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4649,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_row-id',''),(4650,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4651,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_row-class',''),(4652,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4653,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_col-left_0_headline','Caring For Yourself'),(4654,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4655,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_col-left_0_text','It’s also important to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/baby-101/postpartum-care\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">take care of yourself</a> as well as your baby. Use the <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/healthy-postpartum-plate.pdf\" rel=\"\" type=\"application/pdf\">postpartum plate method</a> to be sure you’re following a healthy eating plan.\r\n\r\nWhether or not your period has resumed, the possibility of becoming pregnant exists at any time. Unless you want to become pregnant, use birth control (contraception). If you are not currently on a birth control method, use condoms to avoid pregnancy. To learn more about your options, visit <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/birth-control?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/birthcontrol\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">kp.org/birthcontrol</a> or watch these videos:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/0ycTsYzfXgy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Birth control</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/Ii1wt2s3HKk#/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">IUDs</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/vWAOQ9VUDg7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Nexplanon</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4656,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4657,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_col-left_0_background',''),(4658,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4659,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4660,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4661,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_col-right_0_headline','What If I Start To Feel Stressed?'),(4662,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4663,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_col-right_0_text','Remember, your well-being is affected by both your mind and your body. It’s important to take good care of each to have complete health. Learn how to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/mental-health\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">care for the whole you</a>.\r\n\r\nDepression can occur after your baby is born. This is called <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/baby-101/postpartum-care/pregnancy-depression\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">postpartum depression.</a> It’s common and treatable:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Please watch this fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_912337.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">New Baby and Feeling Depressed?</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Por favor vea esta fotonovela: <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://mydoctor.kaiserpermanente.org/ncal/mdo/presentation/common/healthToolPage.jsp?path=healthtool_912342.xml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Con bebe nuevo, pero deprimida?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKaiser Permanente members have acess to digital mental health and wellness tools at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check out this page</a> for the Calm, Ginger, or myStrength apps. You also can <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for 6-month subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.'),(4664,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4665,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_col-right_0_background',''),(4666,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4667,395,'wellness_layout_topic_8_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4668,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_8_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4669,395,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','How Do I Take Care Of My Body So It Can Nurture My Baby?'),(4670,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4671,395,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','The most important thing at this special time is to prepare and take care of your body. Some of the ways you can prepare your body for nurturing a baby include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/healthy/nutrition\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Eating well</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/maternity/healthy/fitness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Exercising</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.quitting-smoking-and-avoiding-smoke-during-pregnancy.tn7379?kpSearch=smoking%20during%20pregnancy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Not smoking</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFor timely suggestions, check out what\'s happening to <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/care/!ut/p/a0/FchBDsIgEEDRs_QAZIqpRN0BwhUUdhMyQZIyJYRoevvW3X8fIrwhMn5LxlE2xvV0SMSD-qN1yoycdnhBhNg65ooQeBMJ04f-D_soaSUI16e2zqlZGHnXQkp3ljdeWK-smo2_LGqBVuvtp6fpAPoCKk0!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">your baby and your body, week by week</a>.'),(4672,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4673,395,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(4674,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4675,395,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OHIgjP0c24Y'),(4676,395,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','field_6402c9c746e19'),(4677,396,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Quitting Tobacco'),(4678,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(4679,396,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Declare your freedom.\r\n\r\nDevelop a personal strategy for quitting tobacco, and explore the behavior changes that will help you overcome cravings and resist temptations.'),(4680,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(4681,396,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(4682,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(4683,240,'_genesis_title','Quitting Tobacco Resources & Information'),(4684,240,'_genesis_description','If you\'re ready to be free of tobacco, take advantage of these online resources to help you on your journey toward better health. Start today!'),(4685,240,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4686,396,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','240'),(4687,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(4688,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background',''),(4689,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4690,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id',''),(4691,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4692,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class',''),(4693,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4694,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','Are E-Cigarettes A Safe Substitute For Cigarettes?'),(4695,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4696,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','Not enough research has been done to determine if e-cigarettes are a safe alternative to smoking cigarettes. They are not currently regulated. Kaiser Permanente recommends other means of quitting tobacco. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.electronic-cigarettes.abk7152\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Learn more about e-cigarettes</a>.\r\n<h2>Is Social Smoking Ok?</h2>\r\nAny amount of smoking can have an adverse effect on your health. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://smokefree.gov/challenges-when-quitting/cravings-triggers/social-smoking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Social smoking</a> is not safe — and you also put those around in you in jeopardy.'),(4697,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4698,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(4699,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4700,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4701,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4702,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','How Can I Help Myself?'),(4703,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4704,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','There are many ways to help you cope with the process of quitting tobacco.\r\n\r\nUse Cultivating Health(R) <a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/18675-freedom-from-tobacco-ada-locked.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">Freedom From Tobacco</a> to develop a quit program that works for you.\r\n\r\nHelp yourself every step of the way:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.quitting-smoking.qtsmk#aa151596\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Planning your strategy</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.quitting-smoking-coping-with-cravings-and-withdrawal.zp4066\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Handling withdrawal symptoms</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.quitting-smoking-dealing-with-weight-gain.zx3136\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Avoiding weight gain</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nView <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.lung.org/quit-smoking/i-want-to-quit/reasons-to-quit-smoking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">reasons why it\'s worth it to quit tobacco</a>.'),(4705,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4706,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background',''),(4707,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4708,396,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4709,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4710,396,'wellness_layout_topic','a:5:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";}'),(4711,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background',''),(4712,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4713,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id','video'),(4714,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4715,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class',''),(4716,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4717,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_url','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z16vhtjWKL0'),(4718,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_url','field_6402c9c746e19'),(4719,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-video\";}'),(4720,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4721,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','Breaking The Tobacco Habit'),(4722,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4723,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Quitting successfully depends on being ready to change, and on developing new skills and habits.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Video opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z16vhtjWKL0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Watch the video.</a>'),(4724,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4725,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(4726,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4727,396,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4728,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4729,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background',''),(4730,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4731,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id',''),(4732,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4733,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class',''),(4734,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4735,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(4736,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4737,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_text','Sometimes, we all need a little help as we’re working towards a goal. As you work to quit tobacco, a health coach can be a valuable resource in your journey. A health coach can help you determine your patterns and behaviors, set goals, and find new coping strategies.\r\n\r\nLearn more about Kaiser Permanente’s <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching sessions</a>.\r\n<h2>Online Resources To Help You Quit Smoking</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://smokefree.gov/build-your-quit-plan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Quit Plan</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://www.lung.org/stop-smoking/?referrer=https://www.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Stop Smoking</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://www.cdc.gov/tobacco/campaign/tips/quit-smoking/?gclid=CjwKEAjwq6m3BRCP7IfMq6Oo9gESJACRc0bNdRLWlmOL0t14hwIFhdTz55UOsPsU3A2LoviFbwcyjBoCxwPw_wcB\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">How to Quit</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Kaiser Permanente <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/healthylifestyles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">online wellness programs</a> that help you create positive changes in your life</li>\r\n</ul>'),(4738,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4739,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_background',''),(4740,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4741,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4742,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4743,241,'_genesis_title','Quitting Tobacco Resources & Information'),(4744,241,'_genesis_description','If you\'re ready to be free of tobacco, take advantage of these online resources to help you on your journey toward better health. Start today!'),(4745,241,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4746,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_image','241'),(4747,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_image','field_63edb16465fe1'),(4748,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_url',''),(4749,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_url','field_63edb17765fe2'),(4750,396,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(4751,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4752,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(4753,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4754,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id',''),(4755,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4756,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(4757,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4758,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4759,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4760,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4761,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4762,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Looking For More?'),(4763,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4764,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/quitting-tobacco.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">“Freedom from Tobacco” </a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">Telephone coaching</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/tobacco/campaign/tips/quit-smoking/quitstart-app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Free quitSTART mobile app</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://veterans.smokefree.gov/smokeless-tobacco/how-to-quit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Guide to quitting smokeless (chewing) tobacco</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://truthinitiative.org/research-resources/quitting-smoking-vaping/quitting-vaping-here-are-5-tips-handling-nicotine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Tips on quitting vaping</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKaiser Permanente members who need help managing their emotions during quitting have access to digital mental health and wellness tools, at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check out this page</a> for the Calm, Ginger, or myStrength apps. You also can <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for 6-month subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.'),(4765,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4766,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(4767,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4768,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','Are There Medications That Can Help?'),(4769,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4770,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','Medications like Zyban and Chantix can be effective tools for quitting tobacco, particularly when combined with behavioral changes.\r\n\r\nHow do you know if medications are right for you?\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>You have tried on your own to stop smoking, but you were not able to stop.</li>\r\n 	<li>You smoke more than 10 cigarettes a day.</li>\r\n 	<li>You want to increase your chances of quitting smoking.</li>\r\n 	<li>And more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn more about your <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.quitting-smoking-should-i-use-medicine.zw1124?kpSearch=tobacco%20cessation%20medications\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">medication options and if they’re right for you.</a>'),(4771,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4772,396,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(4773,396,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4774,398,'wellness_layout_topic_0_title','Sleep'),(4775,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_title','field_63ed473ac45f4'),(4776,398,'wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','Embrace the day — and the night.\r\n\r\nRest prepares your mind and body to deal with life’s everyday challenges. It’s also important for your overall health. Learn techniques and tips to adjust your lifestyle and relax both mind and body so that you can sleep better.'),(4777,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_subhead','field_63ed4784c45f5'),(4778,398,'wellness_layout_topic_0_background','#006ba6'),(4779,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_background','field_63ed47afc45f6'),(4780,246,'_genesis_title','Getting Better Sleep'),(4781,246,'_genesis_description','Sleep disorders are not uncommon & there are myriad ways to help mitigate the causes & issues associated with the disorder. View helpful online resources!'),(4782,246,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4783,398,'wellness_layout_topic_0_image','246'),(4784,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_0_image','field_63ed4a218c53a'),(4785,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background',''),(4786,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4787,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id',''),(4788,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4789,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class',''),(4790,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4791,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','What Causes Insomnia?'),(4792,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4793,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','Insomnia can be caused by many things. Some triggers are menopause or health problems such as <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-topics/emotional-health/depression/\">depression</a>, <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wellness-topics/emotional-health/anxiety/\">anxiety</a>, and <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.Sleep-Apnea-What-Is-It.abp6071\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">sleep apnea</a>.\r\n\r\nLack of sleep can be dangerous. It can affect your driving, make it difficult to remember things, and more. Some people even stop enjoying being with family and friends.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.insomnia.uh1001?kpSearch=insomnia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Learn more about insomnia</a>.'),(4794,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4795,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background',''),(4796,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4797,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4798,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4799,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','Sleep Resources'),(4800,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4801,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.sleepfoundation.org/sleep-guidelines-covid-19-isolation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Supporting and improving your sleep during the COVID-19 pandemic</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://sleepfoundation.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">National Sleep Foundation</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.sleepapnea.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Sleep apnea help and support</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://healthysleep.med.harvard.edu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">The science of sleep</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://www.webmd.com/sleep-disorders/guide/sleep-disorders-symptoms-types\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Sleep disorders</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"http://sleepeducation.org/essentials-in-sleep/shift-work\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Shift work disorder</a> and <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://www.sleepfoundation.org/shift-work-disorder/shift-work-you/tips-healthy-eating-and-exercising-when-working-shifts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">healthy habits when you work shifts</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),(4802,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4803,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','#e6e6e6'),(4804,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4805,398,'wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4806,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_1_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4807,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background',''),(4808,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4809,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id',''),(4810,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4811,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class',''),(4812,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4813,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','How Do I Get Started?'),(4814,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4815,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','The key to getting more sleep is understanding your night time behaviors. Also, determine what your goals are and how you want to feel. Assess yourself and your situation to plan your path to better sleep.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.insomnia.uh1001?kpSearch=insomnia#uh1001-HealthTools\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Get started by looking at these tools.</a>'),(4816,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4817,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background',''),(4818,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4819,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4820,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4821,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','Could A Health Coach Help Me?'),(4822,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4823,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','Sometimes, we all need a little help as we’re working towards a goal. A health coach can be a valuable resource to help you determine your patterns and behaviors, set goals, and find new sleep strategies.\r\n\r\nLearn more about Kaiser Permanente’s <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">health coaching sessions</a>.'),(4824,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4825,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background',''),(4826,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4827,398,'wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4828,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_2_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4829,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background',''),(4830,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4831,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id',''),(4832,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4833,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class',''),(4834,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4835,247,'_genesis_title','Getting Better Sleep'),(4836,247,'_genesis_description','Sleep disorders are not uncommon & there are myriad ways to help mitigate the causes & issues associated with the disorder. View helpful online resources!'),(4837,247,'_relevanssi_noindex_reason','Relevanssi image attachment filter SEO Framework'),(4838,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','247'),(4839,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','field_63ed558a82b94'),(4840,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url',''),(4841,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_url','field_63ed55a382b95'),(4842,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:11:\"block-image\";}'),(4843,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4844,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','How Can I Get Better Sleep?'),(4845,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4846,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','Your overall health is affected by insomnia and extreme tiredness. Almost everyone experiences this at one point in their lives. There are tips and tricks for better sleep!\r\n\r\nDuring the day:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Wake up the same time every day (even on weekends)</li>\r\n 	<li>Only use your bedroom for sleep (no TV or working!)</li>\r\n 	<li>Get regular exercise — it\'s a great remedy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAt bedtime:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Skip snacks</li>\r\n 	<li>Schedule relaxing evenings</li>\r\n 	<li>Try alternative relaxation tricks (guided imagery, meditation, and more)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLearn more about <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.insomnia-improving-your-sleep.zq1031\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">getting better sleep</a>.\r\n\r\nGet advice, encouragement, and tools with <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/healthy-lifestyle-programs/?kp_shortcut_referrer=kp.org/healthylifestyles\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">online wellness program</a>s that help you create positive changes in your life.'),(4847,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4848,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background',''),(4849,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4850,398,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4851,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_3_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4852,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background',''),(4853,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4854,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id',''),(4855,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4856,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class',''),(4857,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4858,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','Should I Take Herbal Remedies To Help Me Sleep?'),(4859,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4860,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','<a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health/mycare/!ut/p/a0/04_Sj9CPykssy0xPLMnMz0vMAfIjk1PzSlKLrPISS0qLEnN0c1NTMpMz81KL9QuyHRUBGEFCVw!!/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Herbal medicines and supplements</a> such as melatonin and valerian are sold over-the-counter.\r\n\r\nTalk with your doctor before taking any herbal medicines.'),(4861,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4862,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background',''),(4863,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4864,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4865,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4866,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','Relaxation For Living And Sleeping Well'),(4867,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4868,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','Cultivating Health(R) <em>Relaxation for Living and Sleeping Well</em> guides you through several relaxation exercises.\r\n\r\nFind a quiet place where you will not be disturbed. Make yourself comfortable. Take slow, deep breaths. Listen and follow along:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/23QJaMrMPPT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Introduction/welcome</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-welcome-intro-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/HpGxGgKxt5N\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noreferrer noopener\">Daytime relaxation</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-daytime-relaxation-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/seOyacKRciQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noreferrer noopener\">Affirmations</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-affirmations-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/TTNUjo4JV2k\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noreferrer noopener\">Progressive muscle relaxation</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-progressive-muscle-relaxation-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/HKtLAI8YvRc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noreferrer noopener\">Relaxation for sound sleep</a> (<a title=\"PDF document opens in new window\" href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/wp-content/uploads/201805-relaxation-for-sleep-ada-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"application/pdf\">script</a>)</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://kp.qumucloud.com/view/hXxpUv1QqMz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noreferrer noopener\">Surf sounds</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nRelaxation takes practice. The more you do it, the easier it will be to relax.'),(4869,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4870,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background',''),(4871,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4872,398,'wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4873,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_4_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4874,398,'wellness_layout_topic','a:6:{i:0;s:4:\"hero\";i:1;s:3:\"row\";i:2;s:3:\"row\";i:3;s:3:\"row\";i:4;s:3:\"row\";i:5;s:3:\"row\";}'),(4875,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-background',''),(4876,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-background','field_63ed542301f9d'),(4877,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-id',''),(4878,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-id','field_64038036131ce'),(4879,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_row-class',''),(4880,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_row-class','field_64038078131cf'),(4881,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','Should I Take Sleeping Pills?'),(4882,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_headline','field_63ed50d4578b5'),(4883,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','First, talk to your doctor. Sleeping pills can be effective tools when combined with behavioral changes.\r\n\r\nKey points to remember:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sleeping medications are safest if you use them for a short time along with lifestyle changes.</li>\r\n 	<li>They may have side effects, such as daytime drowsiness and nausea.</li>\r\n 	<li>They may not work as well when your body gets used to it.</li>\r\n 	<li>You may have withdrawal symptoms when you stop taking the medicines.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong> </strong><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.za1120#uf10148\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Learn more about taking sleeping pills for insomnia and if it\'s right for you</a>.'),(4884,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_text','field_63ed5109578b6'),(4885,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background',''),(4886,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left_0_background','field_63ed530971fbb'),(4887,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4888,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-left','field_63ed504a8e878'),(4889,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','Looking For More?'),(4890,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_headline','field_63ed522dda19b'),(4891,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/oregon-washington/health-wellness/health-encyclopedia/he.sleeping-better.abo3345\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Some solutions to a good night’s sleep</a></li>\r\n 	<li>If you\'re a Kaiser Permanente Northwest member, talk with your personal doctor about a referral to the Cognitive Behavioral Therapy for Insomnia program.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOr try some apps developed by the Center for Behavioral Health Intervention Technologies, at Northwestern University\'s Feinberg School of Medicine. They are free from Google Play, and include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/thoughtchallenger\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Thought Challenger</a>, to reinforce positive thoughts</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/icope\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">iCope</a>, for encouraging and reassuring messages you create</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/relax\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Purple Chill</a>, for exercises on mindfulness, muscle relaxation, and visualization</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/slumber-time\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Slumber Time</a>, to get a better night’s rest with a bedtime checklist, sleep diary, and customizable alarm</li>\r\n 	<li><a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://intellicare.cbits.northwestern.edu/app/dailyfeats\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Daily Feats</a>, to help you incorporate worthwhile and productive activities into your day</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nKaiser Permanente members have access to digital mental health and wellness tools at no charge. <a title=\"Link opens in new window\" href=\"https://healthy.kaiserpermanente.org/health-wellness/mental-health/tools-resources/digital\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external noopener\">Check out this page</a> for a 1-year subscription to Calm or myStrength. You also can <a href=\"http://local.healthengagement.kaiserpermanente.org/health-coaching/\">call a health coach</a> for 6-month subscriptions to Headspace, Whil, SilverCloud, Woebot, or Thrive.\r\n\r\nYou also can make an appointment with the Kaiser Permanente Northwest Mental Health Department. Call 503-249-3434 or 1-855-632-8280.'),(4892,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_text','field_63ed5236da19c'),(4893,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background',''),(4894,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right_0_background','field_63ed532771fbc'),(4895,398,'wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"block-text\";}'),(4896,398,'_wellness_layout_topic_5_col-right','field_63ed50768e879'),(4899,380,'wellness_layout_topic_3_col-left_0_image','256'),(4900,380,'_wellness_layout_to